#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "<color_light_red>Secronom</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>Secronom</color>"

#. ~ Description for <color_light_red>Secronom</color>
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"<color_red>Brings your Cataclysm experience into a hellish nightmare…</color>\n"
"<color_dark_gray>◆ Not recommended for newbs ◆</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>Note that this mod is currently in <color_light_green>stable</color> state. Bugs rarely appears, but if you encounter one or a recent CDDA update has caused an error, feel free to notify the maintainer by creating an issue on its GitHub repository or by sending a DM on Discord.</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>Add <color_yellow>Secronom+</color> for extended content.</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_red>将你的大灾变体验带入地狱般的噩梦……</color>\n"
"<color_dark_gray>◆ 不建议新手使用 ◆</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>请注意，此模组目前处于<color_light_green>稳定</color>状态。bug很少出现，但若你遇到bug或近期CDDA更新导致错误，请随时通过GitHub仓库提交issue或通过Discord发送DM通知维护者。</color>\n"
"\n"
"<color_light_cyan>添加<color_yellow>Secronom+</color>以获取扩展内容。</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\corpses.json
msgid "corpse"
msgid_plural "corpses"
msgstr[0] "尸体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corpse'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\corpses.json
msgid "A headless dead body of a person. Its wound looks deep and hollow..."
msgstr "一具无头的人类尸体。伤口看起来深邃而空洞……"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "saddler egg"
msgid_plural "saddler eggs"
msgstr[0] "鞍背虫卵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saddler egg'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "Dreadful hairy egg. Dare to eat this!"
msgstr "可怕的毛茸茸的卵。敢吃这个吗！"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "cracked saddler egg"
msgid_plural "cracked saddler eggs"
msgstr[0] "破裂的鞍背虫卵"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': 'cracked saddler egg'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "A baby saddler skitters!"
msgstr "一只鞍背虫幼崽在爬动！"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': 'cracked saddler egg'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "Turns out to be a bad egg!"
msgstr "结果是个坏蛋！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cracked saddler egg'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "Dreadful hairy egg. Use to break it."
msgstr "可怕的毛茸茸的卵。用于打破它。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid "hatched saddler egg"
msgid_plural "hatched saddler eggs"
msgstr[0] "已孵化的鞍背虫卵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hatched saddler egg'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\eggs.json
msgid ""
"A hatched egg of a saddler. It's still covered in slimy green goo, but you "
"see nothing of use of it but to throw away."
msgstr "一个已孵化的鞍背虫卵。它仍覆盖着黏糊糊的绿色黏液，但除了扔掉外，你看不出它有什么用处。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "flesh core"
msgid_plural "flesh cores"
msgstr[0] "血肉核心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh core'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_flesh.json
msgid ""
"A membranous core of the flesh. Very soft and slimy, and seems to not decay "
"on its own."
msgstr "一个血肉的膜状核心。非常柔软且黏滑，似乎不会自行腐烂。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "SS laser rifle"
msgid_plural "SS laser rifles"
msgstr[0] "SS激光步枪"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"Though it was known inferior to other laser rifles, SS laser rifle displays "
"efficiency in barraging shots for cheap UPS charges, along with reduced "
"weight and volume."
msgstr "尽管已知它劣于其他激光步枪，但SS激光步枪在廉价UPS充电下进行连射时表现出高效性，同时重量和体积也有所减少。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步枪"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "SS grenade launcher"
msgid_plural "SS grenade launchers"
msgstr[0] "SS榴弹发射器"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "A simple grenade launcher for the use of exceptional SS grenades."
msgstr "一种简单的榴弹发射器，用于发射特殊的SS榴弹。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "CheyTac M200"
msgid_plural "CheyTac M200"
msgstr[0] "CheyTac M200"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"A large, high precision anti-personnel sniper rifle.  Its large size, "
"recoil, and noise is offset by its damage and range."
msgstr "一种大型、高精度的反人员狙击步枪。其庞大的尺寸、后坐力和噪音被其伤害和射程所抵消。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "CheyTac magazine"
msgid_plural "CheyTac magazines"
msgstr[0] "CheyTac弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'CheyTac magazine'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Standard 7-round box magazine for a CheyTac M200 sniper rifle."
msgstr "CheyTac M200狙击步枪的标准7发盒式弹匣。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Hecate II"
msgid_plural "Hecate II"
msgstr[0] "Hecate II"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"A large and heavy anti-material sniper rifle. Its large size, recoil, and "
"noise is offset by its damage and range."
msgstr "一种大型且沉重的反器材狙击步枪。其庞大的尺寸、后坐力和噪音被其伤害和射程所抵消。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Hecate II muzzle brake"
msgid_plural "Hecate II muzzle brakes"
msgstr[0] "Hecate II枪口制退器"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"A box-shaped muzzle brake distinct to Hecate II sniper rifle. It greatly "
"reduces perceived recoil, but increases both bulk and generated noise."
msgstr "Hecate II狙击步枪特有的盒形枪口制退器。它大大降低了感知后坐力，但增加了体积和产生的噪音。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "muzzle"
msgstr "枪口"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Hecate II magazine"
msgid_plural "Hecate II magazines"
msgstr[0] "Hecate II弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hecate II magazine'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Standard 7-round box magazine for a Hecate II sniper rifle."
msgstr "Hecate II狙击步枪的标准7发盒式弹匣。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "KAC ChainSAW"
msgid_plural "KAC ChainSAWs"
msgstr[0] "KAC ChainSAW"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"The KAC ChainSAW is a light weight machine gun designed to be fired from the"
" hip. It is named before the chainsaw, as if the user is actually wielding "
"an actual chainsaw."
msgstr "KAC ChainSAW是一种设计用于腰射的轻机枪。它以链锯命名，仿佛使用者真的在挥舞一把真正的链锯。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "PSG-1"
msgid_plural "PSG-1"
msgstr[0] "PSG-1"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"The PSG-1 is popular for its performance towards long range acquisition and "
"was commonly used in counter-terrorism for police forces."
msgstr "PSG-1因其在远距离捕获方面的性能而广受欢迎，并常被警察部队用于反恐行动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Walther 2000"
msgid_plural "Walther 2000"
msgstr[0] "瓦尔特2000"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"A semi-automatic bullpup sniper rifle. The usage of .300 winchester magnum "
"made it particularly accurate in extreme distances. Its rarity in the market"
" was crazed by gun nuts as collectibles."
msgstr "一款半自动无托狙击步枪。使用.300温彻斯特马格南弹药，使其在极远距离上尤为精准。它在市场上的稀有性令枪械爱好者为之疯狂，被视为收藏珍品。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Walther 2000 magazine"
msgid_plural "Walther 2000 magazines"
msgstr[0] "瓦尔特2000弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Walther 2000 magazine'}
#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "Standard 6-round box magazine for a Walther 2000 sniper rifle."
msgstr "瓦尔特2000狙击步枪的标准6发盒式弹匣。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "XM556"
msgid_plural "XM556s"
msgstr[0] "XM556"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"The XM556 Microgun is a light-weight machine gun designed to be fired from "
"the hip. It uses a large sum of UPS to function, if so, its electrically-"
"driven gatling system barrages a vast amount of projectile at a glance."
msgstr "XM556微型机枪是一款设计用于腰际射击的轻型机枪。它需要消耗大量UPS才能运作，一旦启动，其电力驱动的加特林系统能在瞬间倾泻大量弹丸。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "XM8"
msgid_plural "XM8s"
msgstr[0] "XM8"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight assault rifle, with shared similarities to the G36 rifle. It "
"is known accurate and modifiable, but requires sustained attention to "
"prevent malfunctions."
msgstr "一款轻型突击步枪，与G36步枪有诸多相似之处。它以精准和可改装性著称，但需要持续维护以防故障。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "ZX-1 Sniper Rifle"
msgid_plural "ZX-1 Sniper Rifles"
msgstr[0] "ZX-1狙击步枪"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"Anti-material sniper rifle, designed for anti-personnel against armored "
"terrorist. capable of piercing even the most thickest metal of armor, this "
"weapon will surely put zombies down to bits, although it requires the user "
"to reload the bullet one by one as it doesn't have magazine system like "
"others."
msgstr ""
"反器材狙击步枪，专为对抗装甲恐怖分子而设计。能够穿透最厚重的金属装甲，此武器无疑能将丧尸撕成碎片，尽管它需要使用者逐发装填子弹，因为它不像其他步枪那样拥有弹匣系统。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "LMI Laser Rifle"
msgid_plural "LMI Laser Rifles"
msgstr[0] "LMI激光步枪"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid ""
"Sleek, futuristic laser rifle, the LMI stands for Living Matter Incinerator,"
" and as the name suggest, capable of delivering superheated laser energy "
"towards zombies and humans. the only warning this weapon has is to not aim "
"it at your eyes."
msgstr "流线型、未来感十足的激光步枪，LMI代表活体焚化器，顾名思义，能够向丧尸和人类释放超高温激光能量。此武器唯一的警告是不要将其对准你的眼睛。"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\secro_guns.json
msgid "semi-auto"
msgstr "半自动"

#: .\Modification Files\Items\-Essentials\secro_items_NPC_missions.json
