#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed wall"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的墙壁"

#. ~ Description for fleshed wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A typical wall, now covered in membranous veins, flesh and swollen warts of "
"some sort."
msgstr "一面典型的墙壁，现在覆盖着膜状血管、肉块和某种肿胀的疣状物。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed window"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的窗户"

#. ~ Description for fleshed window
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Webs of vein blocks the entirety of the glass, making it useless to see "
"through unless you break it."
msgstr "血管网络完全遮挡了玻璃，除非打破它，否则无法看清外面。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed window frame"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的窗框"

#. ~ Description for fleshed window frame
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A window frame, splattered with blood and ripped veins in its jagged shards "
"of glass."
msgstr "一个窗框，其锯齿状的玻璃碎片上溅满了鲜血和撕裂的血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed wood door"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的木门"

#. ~ Description for fleshed wood door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A standard door that is covered in thick, fleshy veins."
msgstr "一扇标准的门，覆盖着厚厚的肉状血管。"

#. ~ Description for fleshed wood door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A standard door that is covered in thick, fleshy veins. You can barely see a"
" deadbolt keyhole, though you can't do anything without removing all the "
"gore sticking into it."
msgstr "一扇标准的门，覆盖着厚厚的肉状血管。你勉强能看到一个门栓锁孔，但如果不清理掉所有堵塞其中的血肉，你什么也做不了。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed floor"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的地板"

#. ~ Description for fleshed floor
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"This floor has been infested by flesh strands, like roots digging deep in "
"small gaps."
msgstr "这块地板已被肉丝侵染，像根须一样深深扎入细小的缝隙中。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed rock floor"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的岩石地板"

#. ~ Description for fleshed rock floor
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Sticky webs of flesh strand reaches down from the ceiling into the floor."
msgstr "粘稠的肉丝网从天花板延伸到地板。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed stairs"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的楼梯"

#. ~ Description for fleshed stairs
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A flight of stairs leading down, except the fact that it is overrun by "
"flesh."
msgstr "一段通往楼下的楼梯，只不过它已被血肉覆盖。"

#. ~ Description for fleshed stairs
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A flight of stairs leading up, except the fact that it is overrun by flesh."
msgstr "一段通往楼上的楼梯，只不过它已被血肉覆盖。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "flesh wart"
msgstr "肉疣"

#. ~ Description for flesh wart
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A tiny wart, but for its size, it can spread a vast amount of noxious gas "
"into the air. Destroying it is a challenge, as it grows back on the spot."
msgstr "一个微小的疣状物，但就其大小而言，它能向空气中释放大量有毒气体。摧毁它是一个挑战，因为它会在原地重新生长。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed dirt"
msgstr "血肉泥土"

#. ~ Description for fleshed dirt
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "It's dirt, but covered in bloody veins."
msgstr "这是泥土，但覆盖着血红的脉络。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "splash"
msgstr "溅洒"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed grass"
msgstr "血肉草丛"

#. ~ Description for fleshed grass
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A cluster of tiny tentacles used to be the wild patch of living grass."
msgstr "一簇细小的触手曾是这片野生的活草。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed long grass"
msgstr "血肉长草"

#. ~ Description for fleshed long grass
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A cluster of long, writhing tendrils about shin high."
msgstr "一簇长长的、扭动的触须，约至小腿高。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed tall grass"
msgstr "血肉高草"

#. ~ Description for fleshed tall grass
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A cluster of tall, writhing tendrils about head high."
msgstr "一簇高高的、扭动的触须，约至头部高。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed shrub"
msgstr "血肉灌木"

#. ~ Description for fleshed shrub
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A small shrub, now a dense tendril cluster."
msgstr "一株小灌木，现已变成密集的触手簇。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "splash."
msgstr "溅洒。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "splat."
msgstr "啪嗒。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed young tree"
msgstr "血肉幼树"

#. ~ Description for fleshed young tree
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Devoured by the flesh, this young sapling has its twigs covered in "
"membranous veins and blood-dripping gore as its leaves."
msgstr "被血肉吞噬，这棵幼树的枝条覆盖着膜状脉络和滴血的肉块作为叶子。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed tree"
msgstr "血肉树"

#. ~ Description for fleshed tree
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A fully grown tree, standing tall even though its already been overwhelmed "
"by the flesh."
msgstr "一棵完全成熟的树，尽管已被血肉淹没，仍屹立不倒。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed flower"
msgstr "血肉花"

#. ~ Description for fleshed flower
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "This flower has fallen to the grasp of the crimson horrors."
msgstr "这朵花已落入猩红恐怖的掌控。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "whish."
msgstr "呼。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed small boulder"
msgstr "血肉小圆石"

#. ~ Description for fleshed small boulder
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A small rock that has succumbed to the flesh."
msgstr "一块已屈服于血肉的小石头。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed medium boulder"
msgstr "血肉中圆石"

#. ~ Description for fleshed medium boulder
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A rock that has succumbed to the flesh."
msgstr "一块已屈服于血肉的石头。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed large boulder"
msgstr "血肉大圆石"

#. ~ Description for fleshed large boulder
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A large rock that has succumbed to the flesh."
msgstr "一块已屈服于血肉的大石头。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\overmap_terrains.json Files\Monsters\Crimson
#: Horrors\Flesh.json
msgid "flesh"
msgid_plural "fleshs"
msgstr[0] "血肉"

#. ~ Description for flesh
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Disgusting mounds of meat, slimy and organic as it seems to live. This "
"pinkish flesh is rotten to the core, and setting it on fire may not be the "
"cure."
msgstr "令人作呕的肉堆，滑腻而有生机，仿佛活着。这粉红色的血肉从核心腐烂，点燃它可能并非解决之道。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "flesh wall"
msgstr "血肉墙"

#. ~ Description for flesh wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Disgusting wall of meat, slimy and organic as it seems to live. This compact"
" lumps of flesh is sinister to the core, and setting it on fire may not be "
"the cure."
msgstr "令人作呕的肉墙，滑腻而有生机，仿佛活着。这团紧实的肉块从核心透着邪恶，点燃它可能并非解决之道。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "vein wall"
msgstr "脉络墙"

#. ~ Description for vein wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A wall composed of vein-like tendrils, seemingly made on the fly."
msgstr "一堵由静脉状触须构成的墙壁，似乎是临时形成的。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "splook!"
msgstr "噗噜！"

#. ~ Description for fleshed tree
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A fully grown tree, standing tall even though its already been overwhelmed "
"by the flesh. Within a closer look, its branches and stems seem to move "
"independently."
msgstr "一棵完全长成的树，尽管已被血肉覆盖，仍屹立不倒。近看之下，它的枝干似乎在独立移动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "veinhole"
msgid_plural "veinholes"
msgstr[0] "静脉孔"

#. ~ Description for veinhole
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A dead veinhole, now a harmless opening revealing a hollow hole. Sure it is "
"gross, but there's no other way..."
msgstr "一个死去的静脉孔，现在只是一个无害的开口，露出中空的洞。虽然很恶心，但别无选择……"

#. ~ Description for veinhole
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A dead veinhole's inner orifice that leads to the surface. Sure it is gross,"
" but there's no other way..."
msgstr "一个死去的静脉孔的内孔，通向地表。虽然很恶心，但别无选择……"

#. ~ Description for veinhole
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"An immature veinhole. It throbs calmly. Sure it is gross, but there's no "
"other way..."
msgstr "一个未成熟的静脉孔。它平静地搏动着。虽然很恶心，但别无选择……"

#. ~ Description for veinhole
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"An immature veinhole's inner orifice that leads to the surface. Sure it is "
"gross, but there's no other way..."
msgstr "一个未成熟的静脉孔的内孔，通向地表。虽然很恶心，但别无选择……"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_ammo_zombie.json
msgid "hatched flesh sack"
msgid_plural "hatched flesh sacks"
msgstr[0] "孵化的血肉囊"

#. ~ Description for hatched flesh sack
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A flesh sack with its vented mouth opened widely. You may want to destroy it"
" as soon as possible."
msgstr "一个血肉囊，其通风口大张。你可能想尽快摧毁它。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "tendril cluster"
msgstr "触须丛"

#. ~ Description for tendril cluster
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A patch of large, writhing tentacles sprouting from both ground and ceiling."
" Within a closer look, these tentacles are trying to form into one. You may "
"want to destroy it as soon as possible."
msgstr "一片从地面和天花板长出的巨大、扭动的触手。近看之下，这些触手正试图融合为一。你可能想尽快摧毁它。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "mouth slit"
msgstr "口缝"

#. ~ Description for mouth slit
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A mouth slit. With enough courage, you can slip through it and will lead you"
" to the depths."
msgstr "一道口缝。若有足够的勇气，你可以滑过它，它将带你深入地下。"

#. ~ Description for mouth slit
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A mouth slit. With enough courage, you can climb up by grabbing at its "
"flabby, slimy flesh edges."
msgstr "一道口缝。若有足够的勇气，你可以抓住它松软、黏滑的血肉边缘爬上去。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "bony outgrowths"
msgstr "骨质增生"

#. ~ Description for bony outgrowths
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A mound of flesh full of prickly sharp bones, emerging from underneath, so "
"watch where you step!"
msgstr "一堆布满尖刺骨头的血肉，从地下冒出，注意脚下！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "tendril outgrowths"
msgstr "触须增生"

#. ~ Description for tendril outgrowths
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A patch of densely-crowded tendrils. These are short, but can grab firmly so"
" watch where you step!"
msgstr "一片密集的触须。它们虽短，但抓握牢固，注意脚下！"

#. ~ Description for flesh
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A thick layer of meat that throbs at a faster rate, yet shares similarities "
"to the normal flesh."
msgstr "一层厚厚的肉，以更快的速率搏动，但与普通血肉有相似之处。"

#. ~ Description for flesh wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Disgusting wall of meat, slimy and organic as it seems to live. This compact"
" lumps of flesh is sinister to the core. This flesh is underdeveloped, and a"
" simple bash would take it down."
msgstr "恶心的肉墙，黏滑而有生机，似乎活着。这团紧凑的血肉从核心透着邪恶。这血肉发育不全，简单一击就能摧毁。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "veinbush"
msgstr "静脉丛"

#. ~ Description for veinbush
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A short, compact bush of living eyed tentacles bursting out of the ground. "
"It stares ominously at the surroundings..."
msgstr "一丛短小、紧凑的活眼触须从地面爆出。它不祥地凝视着周围……"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "gangrenous tumor"
msgstr "坏疽肿瘤"

#. ~ Description for gangrenous tumor
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A large tumor sprouting from the flesh, reeking horrible stench that spreads"
" through a wide area."
msgstr "一个从血肉中长出的巨大肿瘤，散发着可怕的恶臭，弥漫大片区域。"

#. ~ Description for flesh core
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A large slab of flesh that shines a faint, ominous crimson hue."
msgstr "一大块血肉，散发着微弱而不祥的深红色光泽。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed white wall"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的白墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed white wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "Wall painted white, adorned by gore and veins."
msgstr "涂成白色的墙壁，饰以血污和静脉。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed green wall"
msgstr "血肉覆盖的绿墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed green wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "Wall painted green, adorned by gore and veins."
msgstr "涂成绿色的墙壁，饰以血污和静脉。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed red wall"
msgstr "血肉红墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed red wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "Wall painted red, adorned by gore and veins."
msgstr "涂成红色的墙壁，装饰着血肉与血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed blue wall"
msgstr "血肉蓝墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed blue wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "Wall painted blue, adorned by gore and veins."
msgstr "涂成蓝色的墙壁，装饰着血肉与血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed brick wall"
msgstr "血肉砖墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed brick wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A solid brick wall, sturdy enough to support a roof with enough walls and "
"keep out any unwanted visitors."
msgstr "坚固的砖墙，足够支撑屋顶并阻挡任何不速之客。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed stone wall"
msgstr "血肉石墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed stone wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "An even sturdier stone wall covered by the flesh."
msgstr "更坚固的石墙，被血肉覆盖。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed metal bars"
msgstr "血肉金属栅栏"

#. ~ Description for fleshed metal bars
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"Heavy bars overrun by the flesh. Nearly impenetrable due to the thick veins "
"covering it."
msgstr "被血肉侵占的重型栅栏。覆盖其上的厚实血管使其几乎无法穿透。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed glass wall"
msgstr "血肉玻璃墙"

#. ~ Description for fleshed glass wall
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A wall of glass with flesh covering the entirety of its surface, blocking "
"the vision through it."
msgstr "表面完全被血肉覆盖的玻璃墙，阻挡了视线。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed glass door"
msgstr "血肉玻璃门"

#. ~ Description for fleshed glass door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A glass door overrun by the flesh. You can't go through it unless..."
msgstr "被血肉侵占的玻璃门。除非……否则无法通过。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed concrete"
msgstr "血肉混凝土"

#. ~ Description for fleshed concrete
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A concrete with thick, membranous veins all over it."
msgstr "布满厚实膜状血管的混凝土。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed sidewalk"
msgstr "血肉人行道"

#. ~ Description for fleshed sidewalk
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A pavement infected with flesh, with thick veins digging through the cracks."
msgstr "被血肉感染的人行道，厚实血管从裂缝中钻出。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed pavement"
msgstr "血肉路面"

#. ~ Description for fleshed pavement
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A segment of asphalt, with thick veins running across the cracks."
msgstr "一段沥青路面，厚实血管在裂缝间穿行。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed yellow pavement"
msgstr "血肉黄色路面"

#. ~ Description for fleshed yellow pavement
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"The lines of yellow marks are barely visible underneath the thick membranous"
" veins."
msgstr "黄色标记线在厚实膜状血管下几乎看不见。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed concrete floor"
msgstr "血肉混凝土地板"

#. ~ Description for fleshed concrete floor
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A concrete floor with flesh all over it."
msgstr "布满血肉的混凝土地板。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "fleshed ladder"
msgstr "血肉梯子"

#. ~ Description for fleshed ladder
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "A ladder with gore and veins blocking the way."
msgstr "梯子上有血肉和血管阻挡去路。"

#. ~ Description for fleshed stairs
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
