"This is a smartcard reader. Engraved is a text saying \"Secronom Project\" "
"underneath a biohazard symbol. You'll definitely need a special keycard of "
"some sort to unlock the door."
msgstr "这是一个智能卡读卡器。上面刻有文字，在生物危害符号下方写着“Secronom项目”。你肯定需要某种特殊的钥匙卡来解锁这扇门。"

