msgstr "嘎吱！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "whack!"
msgstr "啪！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid "biohazard metal door"
msgstr "生物危害金属门"

#. ~ Description for biohazard metal door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A galvanized steel door, forged to withstand punishment and impede anyone or"
" anything. Typically used in conjunction with automated electronic locking "
"mechanisms that require an external source to unlock. It has a biohazard "
"symbol and a card reader embedded to the door labeled \"Level 1 clearance\"."
msgstr ""
"一扇镀锌钢门，锻造以承受冲击并阻挡任何人或物。通常与自动电子锁定机制配合使用，需要外部来源才能解锁。门上有一个生物危害符号和一个嵌入的读卡器，标有“1级权限”。"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "metal screeching!"
msgstr "金属尖啸声！"

#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
#: Files\Maps\-Essentials\ter_furn.json
msgid "clang!"
msgstr "哐当！"

#. ~ Description for biohazard metal door
#: .\Modification Files\Maps\-Essentials\flesh_ter_furn.json
msgid ""
"A galvanized steel door, forged to withstand punishment and impede anyone or"
" anything. Typically used in conjunction with automated electronic locking "
"mechanisms that require an external source to unlock. It has a biohazard "
"symbol depicting something unearthly on the other side... as the flesh "
"fibers crawl out of the edges. A card reader is embedded to the door, and it"
" requires a special key card for it to open."
msgstr ""
"一扇镀锌钢门，锻造以承受冲击并阻挡任何人或物。通常与自动电子锁定机制配合使用，需要外部来源才能解锁。门上有一个生物危害符号，描绘了另一边某种超自然的存在……因为血肉纤维从边缘爬出。一个读卡器嵌入在门上，需要特殊的钥匙卡才能打开。"

