msgid_plural "shapeshifter's shadowss"
msgstr[0] "变形者的阴影"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "An internal something-something that splits thick, errant shadows."
msgstr "一种内部某物，能分裂出浓密、游移的阴影。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid ""
"An internal something-something that splits thick, errant shadows. This is "
"much less efficient."
msgstr "一种内部某物，能分裂出浓密、游移的阴影。这个效率要低得多。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "fleshknot tentacle cluster"
msgid_plural "fleshknot tentacle clusters"
msgstr[0] "肉结触手簇"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "A cluster of tentacles sent by fleshknot to snare targets."
msgstr "肉结发出的一簇触手，用于缠绕目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "fleshknot tentacle"
msgid_plural "fleshknot tentacles"
msgstr[0] "肉结触手"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "A single tentacle thrust performed by the fleshknot."
msgstr "肉结执行的一次单触手突刺。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "grubby zombie's mouth"
msgid_plural "grubby zombie's mouths"
msgstr[0] "蛆虫僵尸的嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "Spits globs of tainted goo infested with parasites."
msgstr "吐出被寄生虫侵染的污秽粘液团。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "grubby zombie's bloated mouth"
msgid_plural "grubby zombie's bloated mouths"
msgstr[0] "蛆虫僵尸的肿胀嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "Spits larger globs of tainted goo infested with parasites."
msgstr "吐出更大的被寄生虫侵染的污秽粘液团。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "snatcher zombie's mouth"
msgid_plural "snatcher zombie's mouths"
msgstr[0] "攫取僵尸的嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid ""
"Sends off a long-ranged tongue with precise accuracy, stopping the target's "
"movement. Takes a long time to replenish before firing a new one."
msgstr "以精准的准头发射一条长距离舌头，阻止目标的移动。在发射新舌头前需要很长时间补充。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "pellucid zombie's mouth"
msgid_plural "pellucid zombie's mouths"
msgstr[0] "透明僵尸的嘴"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_gun_zombie.json
msgid "An acid-dribbing mouth of a pellucid zombie. Spits concentrated acid."
msgstr "透明僵尸的滴酸嘴。吐出浓缩酸液。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_harvest.json
msgid ""
"With effort, you attempt to collect some worthy byproducts out of the "
"dragon."
msgstr "你努力尝试从龙身上收集一些有价值的副产品。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sacrifice"
msgstr "献祭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sacrifice'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster deals an instant death damage, sacrificing itself upon casting a spell that's been combined with.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者造成即死伤害，并在施放组合法术时牺牲自身。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "null"
msgstr "null"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'null'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "null... just ignore this."
msgstr "null... 忽略此项即可。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Charging Stance"
msgstr "蓄力姿态"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Charging Stance'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sets itself into guarding stance, blocking physical damage while gaining a burst of speed.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者进入防御姿态，格挡物理伤害并获得速度爆发。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid "a spell"
msgstr "一个法术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a spell'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Target spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster locks its line of sight onto the target, then casts the Spell(s).'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的目标法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者锁定目标的视线，然后施放法术。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon Blood Vessel"
msgstr "召唤血管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon Blood Vessel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hands to create a blood vessel.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者引导双手创造一条血管。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon 2 Blood Vessels"
msgstr "召唤2条血管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Blood Vessels'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its core to create 2 blood vessels.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者引导核心创造2条血管。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Blood Vessels'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's blood wave creates 2 blood vessels nearby.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者的血浪在附近创造2条血管。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon Blood Fiend"
msgstr "召唤血魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon Blood Fiend'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's blood wave creates a blood fiend nearby.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者的血浪在附近创造一个血魔。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Blood Curl"
msgstr "血之卷曲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Curl'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'When the target is nearby, caster manipulates some of the blood wave's blood to stick into the target, applying even more bloodbath. This is casted 3 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'当目标靠近时，施法者操纵部分血浪中的血液附着于目标，施加更多浴血效果。此法术施放3次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Blood Wave"
msgstr "血浪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Wave'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its surrounding blood to strike a large area in a cone, dealing moderate bash damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者引导周围血液以锥形区域攻击大范围，造成中等钝击伤害并对所有受影响生物施加浴血效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Explode"
msgstr "爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Explode'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster explodes, dealing bashing damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者爆炸，造成钝击伤害并对所有受影响生物施加浴血效果。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Explode'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently explodes, dealing bashing damage and applying bloodbath to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者猛烈爆炸，造成钝击伤害并对所有受影响生物施加浴血效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Writhing Slash"
msgstr "扭曲斩击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Writhing Slash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the caster's target is nearby after precision stab, the caster's tongue sweeps it sideways, dealing cutting damage and applies an unstable footing to the affected creatures. This is casted for 2 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'若精准刺击后施法者的目标在附近，施法者用舌头横向扫击，造成切割伤害并对受影响生物施加不稳立足效果。此法术施放2次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Precision Stab"
msgstr "精准刺击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Precision Stab'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster reaches and quickly strikes the target with its hideous tongue, dealing moderate stabbing damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者伸出其可怖的舌头快速刺击目标，造成中等穿刺伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Gas Burst"
msgstr "气体爆发"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gas Burst'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the caster's target is upclose, caster sends a strong burst of acidic gas in a wide, yet short cone, dealing moderate acid damage to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'若施法者的目标贴近，施法者释放一股强烈的酸性气体，形成宽而短的锥形区域，对所有受影响生物造成中等酸蚀伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Noxious Gas"
msgstr "剧毒气体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Noxious Gas'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to produce an acidic gas and sends it to the target in a narrow cone that deals lingering acid damage to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者引导身体产生酸性气体，并以狭窄锥形区域射向目标，对所有受影响生物造成持续酸蚀伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Lock On"
msgstr "锁定"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lock On'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster glares at the target, inflicting disorienting impairments.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请改为阅读以下内容：\n"
"'施法者凝视目标，施加迷惑性减益效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Vein Explosion"
msgstr "血管爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vein Explosion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'The torn up ligament explodes internally, dealing an extra bio damage to the target.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'撕裂的韧带在内部爆炸，对目标造成额外的生物伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Volatile Scratch"
msgstr "易爆抓击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Volatile Scratch'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster scratches the target with a claw imbued in volatile bodily fluid, dealing moderate cutting damage that lingers for few turns.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者用浸染易爆体液的爪子抓击目标，造成中等切割伤害，效果持续数回合。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Pull Blood"
msgstr "抽血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pull Blood'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's blood suck pulls in the blood fields. This is casted for 3 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者的吸血能力将血液场吸入。此法术会施放3次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Blood Suck"
msgstr "吸血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Suck'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'More vine strands from the caster sweeps around the vicinity, collecting and sucking the blood fields in which heals the caster.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者更多的藤蔓在周围扫荡，收集并吸收血液场，从而治疗施法者。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Floral Bite"
msgstr "花之咬击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Floral Bite'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'When upclose, caster crunches at the target, dealing extra moderate cutting damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'近距离时，施法者咬碎目标，造成额外的中等切割伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Vine Slash"
msgstr "藤蔓斩击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vine Slash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster strikes the target from afar with its sharp, whip-like vine, dealing small cutting damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者用其锋利的鞭状藤蔓从远处攻击目标，造成少量切割伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon 4 Nautilus Torpedos"
msgstr "召唤4枚鹦鹉螺鱼雷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 4 Nautilus Torpedos'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'After casting sewave, caster creates 4 nautilus torpedos.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施放海波术后，施法者创造4枚鹦鹉螺鱼雷。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sewave"
msgstr "海波术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sewave'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster submerges into the water and generates a seismic wave in a very large cone, dealing cold damage and applying unstable footing to the affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者潜入水中，在极大锥形范围内产生地震波，造成寒冷伤害并使受影响的生物站立不稳。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Restraint"
msgstr "束缚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Restraint'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster latches itself, reducing the agility of the target.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者附着自身，降低目标的敏捷。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Lacerate"
msgstr "撕裂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Lacerate'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the target is nearby, caster slashes with a vine, dealing moderate cutting damage. This is casted 2 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'如果目标在附近，施法者用藤蔓斩击，造成中等切割伤害。此法术会施放2次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Razor Leaf"
msgstr "飞叶快刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Razor Leaf'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"(Combo) spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends its sharp leaves to mince the targets in a line, dealing moderate cutting damage.'"
msgstr ""
"（连击）怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者发射锋利的叶片，在一条线上切碎目标，造成中等切割伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sweet Scent"
msgstr "甜蜜香气"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sweet Scent'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Floral bloom accompanies the wild outburst, spreading sleep-inducing pollens in the same area.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'花朵盛开伴随着狂野生长的爆发，在同一区域散布诱导睡眠的花粉。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Wild Outgrowth"
msgstr "狂野生发"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Wild Outgrowth'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"(Combo) spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to create an outburst of twisted roots and vines under the target, dealing moderate stabbing damage and ensnares all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"（连击）怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者引导身体，在目标下方制造扭曲根须和藤蔓的爆发，造成中等穿刺伤害并缠绕所有受影响的生物。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Summon 2 Triffids"
msgstr "召唤2株三裂植物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Summon 2 Triffids'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hand to create and send forth 2 triffids, along with the wild outgrowth.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者引导其手部创造并派出2株三裂植物，同时伴随狂野生发。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Touch"
msgstr "酸蚀之触"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Touch'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'When upclose, caster then scratches the target with its excess blood, dealing acid damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'近距离时，施法者用其过剩的血液抓击目标，造成酸蚀伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Coat"
msgstr "酸蚀涂层"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Coat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its hands to extract a large amount of acidic fluid from its body, then sends it to the target in a short but wide line, dealing moderate acid damage that lingers overtime.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者通过双手引导，从体内提取大量酸性液体，然后以短而宽的直线射向目标，造成持续的中等酸蚀伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sweepidic"
msgstr "扫荡酸液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sweepidic'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'If the target is nearby, caster sweeps some of the excess fluids in a small cone, dealing small damage to all creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'如果目标在附近，施法者会以小锥形范围扫出部分多余液体，对所有生物造成轻微伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Acid Rain"
msgstr "酸雨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Acid Rain'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its whole body for a very long time to produce an extremely vast amount of corrosive bodily fluids and sends it up above the target then explodes, dealing tremendous acid damage to all creatures in the vicinity, which lingers within time.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者长时间引导全身，产生巨量腐蚀性体液，将其送至目标上方后爆炸，对范围内所有生物造成巨大的酸蚀伤害，并随时间持续生效。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Portal"
msgstr "传送门"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Portal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A multi-dimensional portal is made from the collapse. This portal leads the carrion race into the world.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'坍缩形成了一个多维传送门。这个传送门将腐尸种族引入世界。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Gravitational Collapse"
msgstr "引力坍缩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gravitational Collapse'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'After channeling for a massive amount of time, caster's gravitational force field collapses, creating a supernova, dealing tremendous bash damage to all creatures. Sparkling objects are scattered, which enlightens the area.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'经过长时间引导，施法者的引力场坍缩，产生超新星爆发，对所有生物造成巨大的钝击伤害。散落的闪光物体照亮了区域。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Portal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A multi-dimensional portal is made from the collapse. This portal leads the vector race into the world.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'坍缩形成了一个多维传送门。这个传送门将矢量种族引入世界。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Vectorize"
msgstr "矢量化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vectorize'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'A wave of vector dust spreads from the caster, converting nearby organic terrains such as grass and bushes to become infected.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'一股矢量尘埃从施法者处扩散，将附近的有机地形（如草地和灌木）转化为感染状态。'"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'a spell'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid "The sight of <npcname> locks onto its target..."
msgstr "<npcname>的视线锁定了目标..."

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Morph"
msgstr "形态转变"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Morph'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently morphs into an ichorus.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者猛烈地转变为一只伊科鲁斯。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Morph'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster violently morphs into a psyrus.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者猛烈地转变为一只赛鲁斯。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Cursed Lands"
msgstr "诅咒之地"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cursed Lands'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels itself, creating a lingering curse that calls zeds in its area while enshrouds the caster with the black mist to heal and protect.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者引导自身，创造出一个持续存在的诅咒，召唤区域内的僵尸，同时用黑雾笼罩自身以进行治疗和防护。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Cling"
msgstr "黏附"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Cling'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster leaps onto the target's feet, harming their overall mobility.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者跃向目标的脚部，损害其整体机动性。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Push"
msgstr "暗影推击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Push'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster pushes the targets with its shadows.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者用其暗影推动目标。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Burst"
msgstr "暗影爆发"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Burst'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends out a wave of shadow, dealing moderate bashing damage, applying unstable footing and knocks them back.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者释放出一股暗影波，造成中等钝击伤害，施加不稳立足效果并将其击退。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Sinister Strike"
msgstr "邪影打击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sinister Strike'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster produces a compact shadow, forming a silhouette with its claws imbued in shadows then strikes the target, dealing moderate cutting damage and applying blindness.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者产生一团凝聚的暗影，形成一个爪部浸染暗影的轮廓，然后攻击目标，造成中等切割伤害并施加失明效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Nocturnal Sweep"
msgstr "夜影横扫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Nocturnal Sweep'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster nimbly slashes through the vicinity, dealing moderate cutting damage to the surrounding creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者灵巧地扫过周围区域，对附近的生物造成中等切割伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Shadow Pull"
msgstr "暗影拉扯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Pull'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body to send forth errant shadows to the targets then pulls them in.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者引导身体，向目标释放错乱的暗影，然后将他们拉向自己。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Refleshing Strike"
msgstr "血肉重塑打击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Refleshing Strike'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster stabs a random ally, injecting them with all the excess flesh that heals a tremendous amount of health and increases their body mass.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者随机刺伤一名盟友，注入所有多余的血肉，为其恢复大量生命值并增加其体重。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Reflesh"
msgstr "血肉重塑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reflesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster shoots out tendrils that pierces nearby allies then injecting them with extra flesh, healing a moderate amount of health.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者射出触须刺穿附近的盟友，然后注入额外的血肉，为其恢复中等量的生命值。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Flesh Chunk"
msgstr "血肉块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Flesh Chunk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes a chunk of its own flesh, dealing an enormous amount of damage on itself.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者从自身取下一块血肉，对自己造成巨额伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Stab"
msgstr "触须刺击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Stab'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster sends out a tentacle to pierce at its target, doing a small random stabbing damage. This is casted 4 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者伸出一根触须刺向目标，造成随机的少量刺击伤害。此法术会施放4次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Flurry"
msgstr "触须狂舞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Flurry'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels its body, causing its tentacles to stretch outwards in all directions, dealing stabbing damage to all affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者引导其身体，使触须向四面八方伸展，对所有受影响的生物造成刺击伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Gorespawn"
msgstr "血肉滋生"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gorespawn'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster channels itself to send out giant tendrils more actively, causing the ground to resonate which applies unstable footing to all creatures within its range.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者引导自身更积极地释放巨型触须，引起地面共振，使其范围内的所有生物陷入立足不稳状态。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Terrestrial Destruction"
msgstr "大地毁灭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Terrestrial Destruction'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes down adjacent terrains, destroying them which results into a deep pit.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者摧毁相邻的地形，将其破坏成一个深坑。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tendril Disturbance"
msgstr "触须扰动"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tendril Disturbance'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'From sensing a nearby target, caster sends 1-2 tentacles near them.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者感知到附近的目标后，在其附近释放1-2根触须。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Slam"
msgstr "触须猛击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Slam'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster slams itself to the target, dealing bashing damage.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者猛击目标，造成钝击伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Tentacle Smash"
msgstr "触须粉碎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tentacle Smash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster slams itself to the ground, dealing bashing damage and applying unstable footing to the affected creatures.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者猛击地面，造成钝击伤害并使受影响的生物陷入立足不稳状态。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a spell'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid ""
"Target spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster locks its line of sight onto the target, then randomly casts one of the Spell(s).'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的目标法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者锁定目标的视线，然后随机施放其中一个法术。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Mincemeat Heal"
msgstr "肉糜治疗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mincemeat Heal'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster is healed by 60.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者恢复60点生命值。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Mincemeat"
msgstr "肉糜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mincemeat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster cannibalizes, chomping at itself or an adjacent random ally that heals the caster amplified by 50% of the damage dealt.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者进行同类相食，啃咬自身或相邻的随机盟友，根据造成的伤害的50%额外恢复施法者的生命值。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid "a note"
msgstr "一条注释"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a note'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
#: Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_large.json
msgid ""
"Note spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Provides a notice about the casted spell's result.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的注释法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'提供关于施放法术结果的提示。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Whipslash"
msgstr "鞭笞斩击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Whipslash'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's volatile lump sends forth an errant tendril that strikes the target, dealing cutting damage. This is casted randomly from 2 to 4 times.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代说明：\n"
"'施法者的不稳定肉块释放出一根错乱的触须攻击目标，造成切割伤害。此法术会随机施放2到4次。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Corrupt"
msgstr "腐化"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Corrupt'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's arm biters vomit a corrosive, sticky fluid at the target's area that enslows and constantly damages all creatures who stands on it.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。若你看到此条，请阅读以下说明：\n"
"'施法者的噬臂者向目标区域呕吐腐蚀性粘液，使站立其上的所有生物减速并持续受到伤害。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Stun"
msgstr "核心眩晕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Stun'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster becomes stunned.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。若你看到此条，请阅读以下说明：\n"
"'施法者陷入眩晕状态。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Damage"
msgstr "核心伤害"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Damage'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster takes massive bio damage, along with the constant damaging and crippling effects from the explosion.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。若你看到此条，请阅读以下说明：\n"
"'施法者承受巨额生化伤害，并持续受到爆炸造成的伤害与致残效果。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Core Explosion"
msgstr "核心爆炸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Core Explosion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster's torsal lump suddenly explodes, spreading a large area of corrupted acid and deals tremendous bashing damage that affects all creatures within range. Caster then becomes crippled, rendering it slowed and unconscious for a long time.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。若你看到此条，请阅读以下说明：\n"
"'施法者的躯干肿块突然爆炸，扩散大范围腐蚀酸液，并对范围内所有生物造成巨额钝击伤害。施法者随后陷入残废状态，长时间减速且失去意识。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid "Pin Missile"
msgstr "针刺飞弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Pin Missile'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
