msgstr "阴影笼罩：致盲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Enshroud: Blind'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_smol.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Blinds target for few turns as well.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'同时使目标致盲数回合。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid "Infect"
msgstr "感染"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infect'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster will try to infect the target by dealing 25 biological damage. If the target dies, they succumb to the flesh.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者会尝试感染目标，造成25点生物伤害。如果目标死亡，他们将屈服于血肉。'"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Infect'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_magic_trans.json
msgid ""
"Spell casted by a monster. If you're seeing this, then read this one instead:\n"
"'Caster infects the target, turning them into a crimson horror.'"
msgstr ""
"怪物施放的法术。如果你看到这条信息，请阅读以下替代描述：\n"
"'施法者感染目标，将其转变为猩红恐怖。'"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "<color_magenta>clinger</color>"
msgid_plural "<color_magenta>clinger</color>s"
msgstr[0] "<color_magenta>黏附者</color>"

#. ~ Use action friendly_msg for {'str': '<color_magenta>clinger</color>'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "How the turntables..."
msgstr "风水轮流转……"

#. ~ Use action hostile_msg for {'str': '<color_magenta>clinger</color>'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "The clinger detaches!"
msgstr "黏附者脱落了！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '<color_magenta>clinger</color>'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid ""
"A filthy rotten creature that greatly hampers your reflexes. Activate to "
"pull it off."
msgstr "一种肮脏腐烂的生物，会严重阻碍你的反应能力。激活以将其扯下。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "flesh chunk"
msgid_plural "flesh chunks"
msgstr[0] "肉块"

#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str': 'flesh chunk'}.
#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str': 'cooked flesh chunk'}.
#. ~ Use action activation_message for {'str': 'smoked flesh chunk'}.
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid ""
"<color_light_green>As you chomp down the flesh, your body feels "
"refreshed.</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_green>当你大口吞下这块肉时，身体感到焕然一新。</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh chunk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid ""
"Fresh chunk of meat from the melting flesh you can tell as its precious "
"innard. Both gross and odd looking, but possesses regenerative properties "
"which mends deep wounds when eaten."
msgstr "从融化血肉中取出的新鲜肉块，可辨认出其珍贵的内脏。外观既恶心又怪异，但具有再生特性，食用后可治愈深层伤口。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "cooked flesh chunk"
msgid_plural "cooked flesh chunks"
msgstr[0] "熟肉块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cooked flesh chunk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid ""
"This is a chunk of freshly cooked flesh, though it regenerative properties "
"has dimished significant and tastes the same."
msgstr "这是一块新鲜烹制的肉块，但其再生特性已显著减弱，味道依旧。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "smoked flesh chunk"
msgid_plural "smoked flesh chunks"
msgstr[0] "熏肉块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'smoked flesh chunk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\-Essentials\secro_monitem.json
msgid "A disgusting chunk of flesh that has been smoked for preservation."
msgstr "一块令人作呕的肉块，经过烟熏以保存。"

