#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Ayenel.json
msgid "ayenel"
msgid_plural "ayenels"
msgstr[0] "阿耶内尔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ayenel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Ayenel.json
msgid ""
"A walking flesh sentinel, with huge, sharp blade hanging from its "
"predominant eye. Its extra appendages hang without a certain function."
msgstr "一个行走的肉块哨兵，其突出的眼睛上悬挂着巨大而锋利的刀刃。额外的附肢无特定功能地垂挂着。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'ayenel'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Ayenel.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s glares at %3$s with pure malice!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s以纯粹的恶意瞪着%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Maneater.json
msgid "maneater"
msgid_plural "maneaters"
msgstr[0] "食人者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'maneater'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Maneater.json
msgid ""
"A triffid-looking creature, composed of staggering flesh and bones. Its "
"'flower petals' are lined with razor-sharp teeth, with slender 'vines' "
"twitching incoherently. Unique to its adaptive instincts, its need for "
"'nutrients' drive it to face everything with voracious intent."
msgstr ""
"一个类似三裂植物的生物，由摇晃的肉块和骨骼构成。其'花瓣'边缘布满锋利的牙齿，细长的'藤蔓'无规律地抽搐。独特的适应本能使其对'营养'的需求驱使它以贪婪的意图面对一切。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'maneater'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Maneater.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s slashes %3$s with a sharp tendril!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s用锋利的触须劈砍%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid "shapeshifter"
msgid_plural "shapeshifters"
msgstr[0] "变形者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shapeshifter'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid ""
"An inhumane creature, shrouded in disorienting atmosphere. Its appearance is"
" a complete mystery, neither its true nature."
msgstr "一个非人的生物，笼罩在令人迷失的氛围中。它的外观完全是个谜，其真实本质亦不为人知。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'shapeshifter'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>The air surrounding %1$s intensifies!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s周围的空气变得浓烈！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid "The shapeshifter sends out errant shadows!"
msgstr "变形者释放出飘忽不定的阴影！"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'shapeshifter'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s shifts erratically!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s不规则地变换形态！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json Files\Monsters\Zombies\Zombie.json
msgid "zombie"
msgid_plural "zombies"
msgstr[0] "僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"black eyes. Within a closer look, its visage blurs occasionally."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，油黑的眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。细看之下，其面容偶尔会变得模糊。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid "decayed zombie"
msgid_plural "decayed zombies"
msgstr[0] "腐烂僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'decayed zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Shapeshifter.json
msgid ""
"A once-dead human corpse. Its discolored swollen flesh is riddled with "
"festering wounds and open sores. Within a closer look, its visage blurs "
"occasionally."
msgstr "一具曾经死去的人类尸体。其变色肿胀的肉体布满溃烂的伤口和敞开的疮口。细看之下，其面容偶尔会变得模糊。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Weaver.json
msgid "flesh weaver"
msgid_plural "flesh weavers"
msgstr[0] "织肉者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh weaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Weaver.json
msgid ""
"A large, sentient, beetle-like creature with broad set of claws and "
"appendages, odd to its vile yet pacifistic nature. Merely a lonesome "
"wanderer, and without demise, seeks to tend on an organism's flesh."
msgstr ""
"一只大型、有感知力的甲虫状生物，拥有宽阔的爪子和附肢，与其邪恶却和平的天性形成奇特对比。它只是个孤独的漫游者，在未死亡时，寻求照料生物的血肉。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Abberations\Weaver.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s injects %3$s with a volatile fluid!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s向%3$s注入了一种不稳定液体！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
msgid "secronom dragon"
msgid_plural "secronom dragons"
msgstr[0] "塞克诺龙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'secronom dragon'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
msgid ""
"An inactive cyber dragon, caged in an indestructible tube filled with "
"greenish liquid. Its chainlocked mouth growls, whilst constant beeping noise"
" underneath it is barely heard."
msgstr "一条休眠中的赛博龙，被关在一个装满绿色液体的坚不可摧的管子里。它被锁链锁住的嘴发出低吼，同时底下几乎听不到持续的哔哔声。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'secronom dragon'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'secronom dragon (armed)'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
msgid ""
"This massively armored reptilian has its own purpose: ERADICATION.\n"
"It's the product of technological advancements using mere bionics, altogether with vast weaponry installations to form the \"SAVIOR\"."
msgstr ""
"这只重装甲爬行动物有其自身的目的：根除。\n"
"它是技术进步仅使用仿生学，结合大量武器装置形成的“救世主”产物。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'secronom dragon'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s growls...</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s发出低吼...</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
msgid "secronom dragon (armed)"
msgid_plural "secronom dragon (armed)s"
msgstr[0] "塞克诺龙（武装）"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'secronom dragon (armed)'}"'s spell
#. "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s's reinforcer bots detaches from its hips as it engages for combat!</color>\n"
"<color_dark_gray>The reinforcer bots shoot off and take their distance.</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s的强化机器人从其臀部脱离，准备投入战斗！</color>\n"
"<color_dark_gray>强化机器人射出并拉开距离。</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "reinforcer"
msgid_plural "reinforcers"
msgstr[0] "强化者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reinforcer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A large, disk shaped hovering bot deployed by the cyber-dragon. Carries and "
"deploys various combat drones and robots into the field."
msgstr "一个由赛博龙部署的大型圆盘状悬浮机器人。携带并部署各种战斗无人机和机器人到战场上。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'reinforcer'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s beeps as a robot is deployed!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s发出哔哔声，一个机器人被部署！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "shocker"
msgid_plural "shockers"
msgstr[0] "电击者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shocker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A gyrocoptic ball, enveloped in electrical discharges. Deadly sawblades "
"rotate beneath its metallic body."
msgstr "一个陀螺球体，被电光环绕。致命的锯片在其金属躯体下旋转。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "walker"
msgid_plural "walkers"
msgstr[0] "步行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'walker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A four legged, riot suppressing bot with an automated MP5 mounted as its "
"head. Its feet are tipped with tazers for close combat and/or subduing "
"targets."
msgstr "一个四足防暴机器人，头部装有自动化MP5。其足尖配有电击器，用于近战和/或制服目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "launcher"
msgid_plural "launchers"
msgstr[0] "发射器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'launcher'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid ""
"An automated missile deploying helidrone. It launches homing missiles from "
"its hatch, activating them upon release."
msgstr "一个自动部署导弹的直升机无人机。它从其舱口发射追踪导弹，释放时激活。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'launcher'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s sends out missiles!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s发射导弹！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "homing missile"
msgid_plural "homing missiles"
msgstr[0] "追踪导弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'homing missile'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomDragon_spawns.json
msgid "A heat-seeking missile, about to explode on its hapless target."
msgstr "一枚热追踪导弹，即将在其不幸的目标上爆炸。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#: Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
msgid "laser beam turret"
msgid_plural "laser beam turrets"
msgstr[0] "激光炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser beam turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-L1, also known as Secronom Defense Project Type \"Laser\", is an "
"advanced laser turret based from the miniature TX-5LR Cerberus. Its "
"autonomous laser cannon fires a concentrated beam of pure heat that pierces "
"through targets. Every shot requires an immensive power from its source."
msgstr ""
"SDP-L1，也称为塞克诺防御计划“激光”型，是一种基于微型TX-5LR "
"Cerberus的先进激光炮塔。其自主激光炮发射一道集中的纯热光束，穿透目标。每次射击都需要其能源提供巨大功率。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'laser beam turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#: Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s shoots a ray of heat at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s向%3$s射出一道热射线！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid "electroshock turret"
msgid_plural "electroshock turrets"
msgstr[0] "电击炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'electroshock turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-E3, a highly modified turret developed for immobilizing nearby creatures"
" with the use of its electrifying tesla-coil. Its 360 degree AI sensor cam "
"allows it to identify foes and discharge the turret automatically. Firmly "
"embedded to the terrain, it requires a huge amount of power from its source "
"to operate."
msgstr ""
"SDP-E3，一种经过高度改装的炮塔，旨在利用其带电的特斯拉线圈使附近的生物无法动弹。其360度AI传感器摄像头可识别敌人并自动发射炮塔。它牢固地嵌入地形中，需要从电源获取大量电力才能运作。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'electroshock turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s sends an electric current!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s释放了一道电流！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid "graviton turret"
msgid_plural "graviton turrets"
msgstr[0] "引力子炮塔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'graviton turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
msgid ""
"SDP-G7P, a small turret that disorient movements of its target using strong "
"magnetic fields that is generated under its large, gaping barrel. The turret"
" is slow to recharge and the generated field doesn't last long, as it is a "
"prototype version of its predecessor."
msgstr ""
"SDP-G7P，一种小型炮塔，利用其巨大、敞开的炮管下生成的强磁场扰乱目标的行动。该炮塔充电缓慢，生成的磁场持续时间不长，因为它是其前代的原型版本。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'graviton turret'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s generates a energized field under %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s在%3$s下方生成了一个充能场！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'laser beam turret'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Bots\SecronomTurrets_modded.json
msgid ""
"SDP-L1, also known as Secronom Defense Project Type \"Laser\", is an "
"advanced laser turret based from the miniature TX-5LR Cerberus. Its "
"autonomous laser cannon fires a concentrated beam of pure heat that pierces "
"through targets. It uses a modified storage battery that allows the turret "
"to operate on its own."
msgstr ""
"SDP-L1，又称Secronom防御计划“激光”型，是一种基于微型TX-5LR "
"Cerberus的先进激光炮塔。其自主激光炮发射一道集中的纯热光束，可穿透目标。它使用改良的蓄电池，使炮塔能够独立运作。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid "amalgam stinger"
msgid_plural "amalgam stingers"
msgstr[0] "融合毒刺怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'amalgam stinger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid ""
"A rotten conglomeration of fused limbs and appendages that has been formed "
"into a stout, meandering humanoid. Several parts of its body are infused "
"with bulbous warts, to which are seem to be filled with sizzling crimson "
"acid. A slender, predominant limb sways like a whip, flowing freely around "
"itself. It is tipped with a barbed stinger that drips with a potent "
"corrosive compound."
msgstr ""
"一堆腐烂的融合肢体与附肢，形成了一个粗壮、蜿蜒的人形生物。其身体多处布满球状疣，里面似乎充满了嘶嘶作响的深红色酸液。一条细长的主要肢体像鞭子一样摇摆，在自身周围自由流动。末端带有一根带刺的毒刺，滴落着强效腐蚀性化合物。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'amalgam stinger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s twitches violently as it glares at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s剧烈抽搐，怒视着%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid "amalgam ravager"
msgid_plural "amalgam ravagers"
msgstr[0] "融合破坏者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'amalgam ravager'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous humanoid formed by fusing several appendages of unknown "
"creatures, which are reemerging back and forth in its vessel. Apart from its"
" figure are long, irregular bone outgrowths covering its surface, and a "
"gaping jaw opened widely on its twisted visage. Sluggish, yet opposes great "
"danger."
msgstr ""
"一个由未知生物的多个附肢融合而成的恐怖人形生物，这些附肢在其容器中来回重新浮现。除了其身形外，表面覆盖着长而不规则的骨刺，扭曲的面容上张开着大嘴。行动迟缓，却构成巨大威胁。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'amalgam ravager'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s's bone outgrowth extends!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s的骨刺延伸了！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid "amalgam scavenger"
msgid_plural "amalgam scavengers"
msgstr[0] "融合拾荒者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'amalgam scavenger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
msgid ""
"A fleshed amalgamation consists mostly of thin and slender appendages, with "
"a throbbing core on its thorax. It glows ominously. Docile and cautious, in "
"contrast to its horrifying figure."
msgstr "一种肉质的融合体，主要由细长的附肢组成，胸部有一个搏动的核心，散发着不祥的光芒。与其恐怖的外形相反，它温顺而谨慎。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'amalgam scavenger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s flees from %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s逃离了%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam_spawns.json
#: Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid "fleshling"
msgid_plural "fleshlings"
msgstr[0] "肉块怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fleshling'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A tiny slab of meat that moves by either hopping or slithering through the "
"ground. It throbs faster as it gets closer."
msgstr "一小块会通过跳跃或在地面滑行移动的肉片。它越靠近，搏动得越快。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'fleshling'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam_spawns.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s explodes into gore!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s爆炸成血肉碎片！</color>"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'fleshling'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam_spawns.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s explodes into a heap of bladed tentacles!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 爆裂成一堆带刃的触手！</color>"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'fleshling'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Amalgam_spawns.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s sticks on %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 粘附在 %3$s 上！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
msgid ""
"A gargantuan lump of meat, pulsating in faint, velvety hue. Thick, numerous "
"veins penetrate the walls, in every beat causes the surrounding flesh to "
"undulate."
msgstr "一团巨大的肉块，以微弱的天鹅绒色调脉动着。粗壮而繁多的血管穿透墙壁，每一次搏动都使周围的肉体起伏波动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'wall of flesh'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh heap (unifier)'}"'s spell
#. "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
#: Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s trembles!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 颤抖着！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
msgid ""
"A gargantuan lump of meat, throbbing in faint, velvety hue. Thick tentacles "
"pierces through the walls that extends further into the ground, in each "
"rhythmic beats causes all connected veins to pulse."
msgstr "一团巨大的肉块，以微弱的天鹅绒色调悸动着。粗壮的触手刺穿墙壁，进一步延伸至地面，每一次有节奏的搏动都使所有相连的血管随之脉动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s trembles, pounding everything with its tentacles!\n"
"%1$s's tendrils pierces %3$s!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s 颤抖着，用触手猛击一切！\n"
"%1$s 的触须刺穿了 %3$s！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
msgid ""
"A gargantuan lump of meat, pulsating in faint, velvety hue. Several veins "
"protrude from its body that unifies with the surrounding walls."
msgstr "一团巨大的肉块，以微弱的天鹅绒色调脉动着。数条血管从其身体突出，与周围的墙壁融为一体。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s thrashes a tentacle at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 向 %3$s 甩出一条触手！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\FleshVeins.json
msgid "vein beast"
msgid_plural "vein beasts"
msgstr[0] "血管兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vein beast'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\FleshVeins.json
msgid ""
"A cluster of veins formed into a horrendous creeping abomination. Thick "
"strands of membranous vine-like tendrils reaches out of its beating core."
msgstr "一团血管聚集成骇人的爬行怪物。粗壮的膜状藤蔓般触须从其搏动的核心向外延伸。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vein beast'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\FleshVeins.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s sweeps its tendrils onto %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 将触须扫向 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\FleshVeins.json
msgid "rumbler"
msgid_plural "rumblers"
msgstr[0] "隆隆怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rumbler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\FleshVeins.json
msgid ""
"A thick group of veins unified into a crawling nightmare. Large, amalgous "
"core is visible to its predominant limb, and tendrils seemingly gathers "
"around it."
msgstr "一团粗厚的血管群聚合成了爬行的噩梦。其主导肢体上可见巨大的融合核心，触须似乎围绕其聚集。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "eye sprout"
msgid_plural "eye sprouts"
msgstr[0] "眼球芽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'eye sprout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"An eyeball reemerging back and forth from the ground, occasionally peeking "
"at the vicinity. You might want to poke it."
msgstr "一颗眼球在地面来回浮现，偶尔窥视四周。你或许想戳它一下。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'eye sprout'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s writhes, sending crimson horrors to confront "
"%3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 扭动着，释放出猩红恐怖之物对抗 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "flesh tendril"
msgid_plural "flesh tendrils"
msgstr[0] "血肉触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh tendril'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"A thick strand of vein sprouting from the ground. It is tipped with a barbed"
" lasher."
msgstr "一束粗大的血管从地面冒出，末端带有带刺的鞭状结构。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh tendril'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s slashes %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 劈砍 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "jawed flesh"
msgid_plural "jawed fleshs"
msgstr[0] "颚化血肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jawed flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"An oddly formed orifice that has emerged as an outgrowth of the flesh, with "
"rows of bones surrounding the gap. Its small, yet powerful jaws can render a"
" target immobilized."
msgstr "一个形态奇特的孔口，作为血肉的增生体出现，裂口周围环绕着成排的骨骼。其虽小却有力的颚部能使目标动弹不得。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'veinhole'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"A large mouth protruding from the flesh, accompanied by numerous viscious "
"tendrils sticking out from its sides."
msgstr "一张巨大的嘴从血肉中突出，两侧伸出无数凶恶的触须。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "flesh sack"
msgid_plural "flesh sacks"
msgstr[0] "血肉囊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh sack'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"A large, bulbous pus sticking firmly to nearby terrains. Distinct to its "
"vented mouth, it throbs at a constant rate as if it's about to hatch..."
msgstr "一个巨大、球状的脓疱紧紧附着在附近的地形上。其通风口般的嘴部特征明显，以恒定频率搏动着，仿佛即将孵化……"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh sack'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s bursts, giving birth to parasytes!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 爆裂开来，诞下寄生体！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "parasyte"
msgid_plural "parasytes"
msgstr[0] "寄生体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'parasyte'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"Frail yet nimble, this scorpion/spider hybrid shows predatory nature by "
"leaping into its prey, despite the fact it just recently pop out from the "
"sack."
msgstr "这种蝎子/蜘蛛混合体虽脆弱却敏捷，展现出掠食本性，会跃向猎物——尽管它刚从囊中破出不久。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid "veinstalk"
msgid_plural "veinstalks"
msgstr[0] "脉管茎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'veinstalk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
msgid ""
"A large, fleshy tendril sprouting from the ground. Tipped with a predominant"
" eye, it sways and occasionally twitches into a particular direction."
msgstr "一根巨大的肉质触须从地面冒出，顶端长着一只显眼的眼睛，它摇摆着并偶尔朝特定方向抽搐。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'veinstalk'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_biome.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s twitches violently...</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s 剧烈地抽搐着……</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid "vessel experimental"
msgid_plural "vessel experimentals"
msgstr[0] "实验型容器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vessel experimental'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid ""
"A human who fell and succumbed to the flesh vessel exoskeleton - an "
"experimental battle suit developed by the Secronom Project. It has "
"completely fused with the body, and seem to have full control over it."
msgstr "一个倒下并屈服于血肉容器外骨骼的人类——这是Secronom项目开发的实验性战斗服。它已与身体完全融合，似乎能完全控制宿主。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vessel experimental'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s aims at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s 瞄准了 %3$s！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vessel experimental'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
msgid ""
"A human who fell and succumbed to the flesh vessel exoskeleton - an "
"experimental battle suit developed by the Secronom Project - and by the "
"looks of it, the body has been recently devoured. Strands of flesh writhe "
"incessantly around it."
msgstr ""
"一个倒下并屈服于血肉容器外骨骼的人类——这是Secronom项目开发的实验性战斗服——从外观判断，其身体最近刚被吞噬。血肉细丝在周围不停地扭动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vessel experimental'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_experimental.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_magenta>A gunner armament emerges from %1$s's body, aiming at "
"%3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>一门枪械武装从 %1$s 体内浮现，瞄准了 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "black bear cub"
msgid_plural "black bear cubs"
msgstr[0] "黑熊幼崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'black bear cub'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A juvenile American black bear.  This one isn't much of a threat, but be wary of its parent; black bears are known for their protectiveness.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一只美洲黑熊幼崽。它本身威胁不大，但要警惕其父母；黑熊以保护幼崽而闻名。\n"
"被血肉感染后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "black bear"
msgid_plural "black bears"
msgstr[0] "黑熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'black bear'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The American black bear.  A large omnivorous scavenger, it has powerful claws and jaws, and is an effective ambush hunter.  Most individuals are shy around humans, but they're fiercely protective of their cubs.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"美洲黑熊。这是一种大型杂食性清道夫，拥有强壮的爪子和颚部，是高效的伏击猎手。大多数个体对人类保持警惕，但会拼命保护幼崽。\n"
"被血肉感染后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "black rat"
msgid_plural "black rats"
msgstr[0] "黑鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'black rat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The black rat, an omnivorous rodent with sheer black fur and a long, rough tail.  Harbinger of pestilence, famine, and mange, it will sometimes swarm over the dead or dying.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"黑鼠，一种杂食性啮齿动物，拥有纯黑的皮毛和一条粗糙的长尾。作为瘟疫、饥荒与疥癣的先兆，它们有时会成群结队地涌向死者或垂死之物。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "cougar"
msgid_plural "cougars"
msgstr[0] "美洲狮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cougar'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The Eastern cougar, a large feline predator.  Once thought extinct in this region, conservation efforts were successful in restoring a thriving population.  Fast and silent, this predator can cover long distances with powerful leaps and pounces, catching its prey with its deadly claws before delivering the finishing blow with its enormous fangs.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"东部美洲狮，一种大型猫科掠食者。曾被认为在此区域灭绝，但保护努力成功恢复了其繁荣的种群。这种掠食者迅捷而无声，能以强有力的跳跃和猛扑跨越长距离，先用致命的利爪抓住猎物，再用巨大的獠牙给予致命一击。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "moose"
msgid_plural "mooses"
msgstr[0] "驼鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'moose'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The Eastern moose, the largest living species of deer.  While they aren't aggressive unless angered, the mating season can make the bulls quite ill-tempered.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"东部驼鹿，现存最大的鹿科物种。虽然它们除非被激怒否则并不具有攻击性，但发情期的雄鹿会变得相当暴躁。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "beaver"
msgid_plural "beavers"
msgstr[0] "河狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'beaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The North American beaver, the continent's largest rodent.  Its paddle-shaped tail helps ferry it through the water, and its prominent teeth can chew through wood, which it uses to build dam-like nests in lakes and streams.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"北美河狸，该大陆上最大的啮齿动物。其桨状的尾巴帮助它在水中穿行，突出的牙齿能啃穿木头，用于在湖泊与溪流中建造水坝般的巢穴。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "wild boar piglet"
msgid_plural "wild boar piglets"
msgstr[0] "野猪幼崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wild boar piglet'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wild boar'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"Originally not native in the US, this wild omnivore is a crossbreed between the Eurasian wild boar escaped from hunting reserves and the domesticated pig went feral in the wilderness.  Its population has skyrocketed in the US during the last few decades.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"这种野生杂食动物原非美国本土物种，是欧亚野猪从狩猎保护区逃逸后与野外驯化家猪杂交的产物。过去几十年间，其种群数量在美国激增。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
