msgid ""
"A cuddly kitten of unknown breed, meowing and scampering amidst the death.  Currently feral.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend.."
msgstr ""
"一只品种不明的可爱小猫，在死亡之中喵喵叫着、四处乱窜。目前处于野生状态。\n"
