msgid_plural "cows"
msgstr[0] "奶牛"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "coyote"
msgid_plural "coyotes"
msgstr[0] "郊狼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'coyote'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The Eastern coyote, also called the tweed wolf, is a territorial canine descended from the offspring of gray wolves and true coyotes.  It is intimidated by humans and other predators, but it will still fight if threatened, and the Cataclysm has made it more fearless than usual.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"东部郊狼，亦称特威德狼，是一种领地性犬科动物，由灰狼与纯种郊狼的后代演化而来。它通常畏惧人类和其他掠食者，但受到威胁时仍会战斗，而大灾变使其比往常更加无畏。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
