msgid_plural "fawns"
msgstr[0] "幼鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fawn'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A juvenile northern woodland white-tailed deer, a quick and strong grazing animal.  Favored prey of coyotes, wolves, and giant spider mutants.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一只幼年的北方林地白尾鹿，一种迅捷而强壮的食草动物。是郊狼、狼群以及巨型蜘蛛突变体偏爱的猎物。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

