#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A fox with a bloodshot fur... literally.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一只皮毛布满血丝的狐狸……字面意义上的。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生灵不再如动物般行动，而是化作了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "groundhog"
msgid_plural "groundhogs"
msgstr[0] "土拨鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'groundhog'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"Also known as the woodchuck, this ground squirrel has no actual talent for chucking wood.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"又称旱獭，这种地松鼠实际上并无抛掷木材的本领。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这只曾经的生物不再作为动物行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "horse"
msgid_plural "horses"
msgstr[0] "马"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'horse'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A hooved grazing mammal with a mane of hair, a sweeping tail, and powerful-looking muscles.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种有蹄的食草哺乳动物，拥有鬃毛、扫帚般的尾巴和强健的肌肉。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这只曾经的生物不再作为动物行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "lemming"
msgid_plural "lemmings"
msgstr[0] "旅鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lemming'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The Northern bog lemming, a small, predominantly vegetarian rodent that spends its life in the murk of swamps and other wetlands.  Contrary to popular belief, these creatures are not particularly hapless or suicidal, but they can eat themselves into scarcity within a few generations.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"北方沼泽旅鼠，一种小型、主要以植物为食的啮齿动物，一生都在沼泽和其他湿地的阴暗环境中度过。与普遍认知相反，这些生物并非特别不幸或具有自杀倾向，但它们能在几代内因过度繁殖而耗尽资源。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这只曾经的生物不再作为动物行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "mink"
msgid_plural "minks"
msgstr[0] "水貂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mink'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The American mink, a partially aquatic weasel, once factory-farmed for its fur.  It is a capable fisher, but the presence of otters in these parts makes it rely more on food from the land.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"美洲水貂，一种半水栖的鼬类，曾因其皮毛而被工厂化养殖。它是能干的捕鱼者，但由于该地区存在水獭，它更依赖陆地上的食物来源。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这只曾经的生物不再作为动物行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "muskrat"
msgid_plural "muskrats"
msgstr[0] "麝鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'muskrat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A large omnivorous rodent with a thick furry pelt, found in wetlands across the northern hemisphere.  It marks its territory with a musky odor for which it is named.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种大型杂食性啮齿动物，拥有浓密的毛皮，分布于北半球的湿地。它以其命名的麝香气味标记领地。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这只曾经的生物不再作为动物行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "gigantic naked mole-rat"
msgid_plural "gigantic naked mole-rats"
msgstr[0] "巨型裸鼹鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gigantic naked mole-rat'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A huge, rumbling mutated mass of wrinkly, nearly translucent skin that has been toughened by constant tunneling.  Its hide is riddled with giant scabs, as a pair of incisors the size of an industrial excavator's buckets gnash constantly and several car-length whiskers twitch in the air.  It regularly makes high-pitched chirps as it roams around.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一团巨大、隆隆作响的变异肉块，布满褶皱，皮肤近乎透明，因持续挖掘而变得坚韧。它的表皮布满巨大的疮痂，一对门齿大如工业挖掘机的铲斗，不断咬合，几根汽车长度的胡须在空中颤动。它在游荡时经常发出尖锐的吱吱声。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "opossum"
msgid_plural "opossums"
msgstr[0] "负鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'opossum'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The Virginia opossum, a small omnivorous marsupial native to North America.  About the size of a cat, it is hardy and adaptive, and a fairly common sight in urban areas.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"弗吉尼亚负鼠，一种原产于北美洲的小型杂食性有袋动物。体型约如猫般大小，适应力强且坚韧，在城市地区相当常见。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "otter"
msgid_plural "otters"
msgstr[0] "水獭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'otter'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The North American river otter is a shy water dwelling relative of the weasel, living in large families along the banks of streams.  It is an excellent fisher and a resourceful survivor, using the abandoned dens of beavers and other animals to raise its own young.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"北美河獭是鼬科动物中一种害羞的水生近亲，以大家族形式生活在溪流岸边。它是出色的捕鱼者，也是足智多谋的生存专家，会利用海狸和其他动物废弃的洞穴来抚育幼崽。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "piglet"
msgid_plural "piglets"
msgstr[0] "小猪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'piglet'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A domesticated omnivore descended from the wild boar, intelligent and inquisitive.  Left to its own devices, it has gone feral.  Unlike the fully grown version it can be tamed.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种由野猪驯化而来的杂食动物，聪明且好奇。放任自流后，它已变得野性难驯。与成年个体不同，它可以被驯服。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "pig"
msgid_plural "pigs"
msgstr[0] "猪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pig'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A domesticated omnivore descended from the wild boar, intelligent and inquisitive.  Left to its own devices, it has gone feral.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种由野猪驯化而来的杂食动物，聪明且好奇。放任自流后，它已变得野性难驯。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "rabbit"
msgid_plural "rabbits"
msgstr[0] "兔子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rabbit'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A small mammal with a cute wiggling nose, cotton tail, and made of delicious flesh.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种小型哺乳动物，有着可爱的抽动鼻子、棉花般的尾巴，以及美味的肉质。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "raccoon"
msgid_plural "raccoons"
msgstr[0] "浣熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'raccoon'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A small mammal native to North America, distinctive for its dexterous paws and facial markings.  It is resourceful and agile enough to open sealed containers with its paws.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种原产于北美洲的小型哺乳动物，以其灵巧的爪子和面部斑纹而著称。它足智多谋且敏捷，能用爪子打开密封的容器。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "lamb"
msgid_plural "lambs"
msgstr[0] "羔羊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lamb'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A timid, hooved grazing mammal, and one of the first animals ever domesticated.  Its body is covered in a thick layer of wool, and the males have long, spiraling horns.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种胆小的有蹄食草哺乳动物，是最早被驯化的动物之一。它的身体覆盖着厚厚的羊毛，雄性长有螺旋状的长角。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "sheep"
msgid_plural "sheep"
msgstr[0] "绵羊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sheep', 'str_pl': 'sheep'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A timid, hooved grazing mammal, and one of the first animals ever domesticated.  Its body is covered in a thick layer of wool, and the males have long, spiralling horns.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种胆小的有蹄食草哺乳动物，是最早被驯化的动物之一。它的身体覆盖着厚厚的羊毛，雄性长有螺旋状的长角。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "squirrel"
msgid_plural "squirrels"
msgstr[0] "松鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'squirrel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A small granivorous rodent with a long bushy tail, often seen darting amid the branches of trees.  A skittish varmint with an expression of unwavering austerity, it is the mortal enemy of cat and dog alike.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种小型食谷啮齿动物，长着蓬松的长尾巴，常见于树枝间穿梭。它是一种胆小的害兽，表情严肃坚定，是猫和狗共同的死敌。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "weasel"
msgid_plural "weasels"
msgstr[0] "鼬鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'weasel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"The long-tailed weasel, a small but ubiquitous predator whose range extends across the continent.  It forms its den in small burrows, preferring to occupy the nesting holes of its prey.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"长尾鼬，一种体型虽小但分布广泛的捕食者，活动范围遍及整个大陆。它在小型洞穴中筑巢，偏好占据猎物的巢穴。\n"
"被血肉侵蚀后，这只曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "wolf"
msgid_plural "wolves"
msgstr[0] "狼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wolf', 'str_pl': 'wolves'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"A cunning pack predator, once extinct in the New England area, the wolf was successfully reintroduced and their numbers reached record highs in the decade before the Cataclysm.  Lucky you.\n"
"Infested by flesh, this once living creature no longer act as an animal, but a bloodthirsty fiend."
msgstr ""
"一种狡猾的群体捕食者，曾在新英格兰地区灭绝，狼群被成功重新引入，其数量在大灾变前的十年间达到历史新高。你真走运。\n"
"被血肉侵染后，这曾经的生物不再像动物般行动，而是变成了嗜血的恶魔。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid "Reindeer"
msgid_plural "Reindeers"
msgstr[0] "驯鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Reindeer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_live.json
msgid ""
"Also known as the Caribou, this deer is native to North America and parts of"
" Eurasia, although usually friendly, they can be aggressive during mating "
"season as well as when hungry, something seems off about this one and it "
"seems more hostile than normal."
msgstr ""
"也被称为北美驯鹿，这种鹿原产于北美和欧亚部分地区，虽然通常友好，但在交配季节或饥饿时可能变得具有攻击性。这只似乎有些不对劲，表现得比正常情况更具敌意。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid "SP Experimental Mech \"Flesh\""
msgid_plural "SP Experimental Mech \"Flesh\"s"
msgstr[0] "SP实验机甲“血肉”"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SP Experimental Mech "Flesh"'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid ""
"This experimental mech type \"Flesh\" is the most recent (and last) mechsuit"
" produced by the engineers of the Secronom Project. Very scarce and limited "
"to military use only, it was designed to take on the main force of the "
"battlefield thanks to its exotic yet nigh indestructible material, "
"especially supplemented with a variety of gun morphs. Unfortunately, it "
"requires one to wear a bio-organic power and link it with the mech to accept"
" you as its rider."
msgstr ""
"这款实验型机甲“血肉”是Secronom项目工程师制造的最新（也是最后）的机甲服。数量极为稀少且仅限于军事用途，它被设计用于应对战场主力，这得益于其奇特且近乎坚不可摧的材料，特别是辅以多种枪械变形能力。不幸的是，它需要穿戴者配备生物有机动力装置，并将其与机甲链接以接受你作为骑手。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'SP Experimental Mech "Flesh"'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_mech.json
msgid ""
"This experimental mech type \"Flesh\" is the most recent (and last) mechsuit"
" produced by the engineers of the Secronom Project. Very scarce and limited "
"to military use only, it was designed to take on the main force of the "
"battlefield thanks to its exotic yet nigh indestructible material, "
"especially supplemented with a variety of gun morphs."
msgstr ""
"这款实验型机甲“血肉”是Secronom项目工程师制造的最新（也是最后）的机甲服。数量极为稀少且仅限于军事用途，它被设计用于应对战场主力，这得益于其奇特且近乎坚不可摧的材料，特别是辅以多种枪械变形能力。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid "taken"
msgid_plural "takens"
msgstr[0] "被吞噬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'taken'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A membranous pod of flesh, filled with putrid yellow-ish fluid. Hanging from"
" the ceiling, a creature seems to be trapped inside, but unknown to what it "
"is."
msgstr "一个充满腐臭黄色液体的肉质膜囊。悬挂在天花板上，似乎有生物被困在其中，但未知其为何物。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'taken'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>The taken bursts, letting loose of its content!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>被吞噬者爆裂开来，释放出其中的内容物！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'taken'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid ""
"A membranous pod of flesh, filled with putrid yellow-ish fluid. Sprouting "
"from the flesh, a creature seems to be trapped inside, but unknown to what "
"it is."
msgstr "一个充满腐臭黄色液体的肉质膜囊。从血肉中萌发而出，似乎有生物被困在其中，但未知其为何物。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid "wall of flesh"
msgid_plural "wall of fleshs"
msgstr[0] "血肉之墙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wall of flesh'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_spawns.json
msgid ""
"Thick, lumps of meat taken control by the flesh. It slowly protrudes from "
"the wall, creating fleshed barriers on its way."
msgstr "厚实的肉块被血肉控制。它缓慢地从墙壁中凸出，沿途形成血肉屏障。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "flesh zombie"
msgid_plural "flesh zombies"
msgstr[0] "血肉僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A corpse devoured by the flesh, with complete manipulation over its mindless"
" thoughts."
msgstr "一具被血肉吞噬的尸体，其无意识的思维被完全操控。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "flesh heap"
msgid_plural "flesh heaps"
msgstr[0] "血肉堆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"An enormous outgrowth of flesh with numerous putrid corpses unified in its "
"edges. Dribbling blood seeps from the mouth of the zombies."
msgstr "一个巨大的血肉增生体，边缘融合了众多腐烂的尸体。滴落的血液从僵尸的口中渗出。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh heap'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s pulsates...</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s脉动着...</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "tough zombie"
msgid_plural "tough zombies"
msgstr[0] "强壮僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tough zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Once an athletic human, now a brutal monster. Its facial features are twisted into an expression of pure rage.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"曾是健壮的人类，如今是残暴的怪物。其面部特征扭曲成纯粹的愤怒表情。\n"
"膜状静脉覆盖了其大部分表面，以恒定节奏脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "fat zombie"
msgid_plural "fat zombies"
msgstr[0] "肥胖僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fat zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Stumbling as it moves, this corpse of an overweight human regards its surroundings with an empty black gaze.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这具超重人类的尸体移动时步履蹒跚，空洞的黑色目光扫视着周围环境。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "skeleton"
msgid_plural "skeletons"
msgstr[0] "骸骨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skeleton'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A monstrous overgrowth of ossified tissue has replaced this zombie's rotting skin with an organic armor of dense bone.  Large clumps of black goo seep from its joints as it shambles aimlessly, with sickening crackling sounds filling the air around it.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"畸形的骨化组织过度生长，取代了这只僵尸的腐烂皮肤，形成了一层致密骨骼的有机装甲。大团黑色粘液从其关节渗出，它漫无目的地蹒跚而行，周围空气中充斥着令人作呕的噼啪声。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "spitter zombie"
msgid_plural "spitter zombies"
msgstr[0] "喷吐僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spitter zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A hunched human body with its eyes pushed up into its forehead and drooping cheeks, most of its face is occupied by a puckered mouth. Its stomach is swollen and nearly translucent, with a sickly velvet tint.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具佝偻的人体，眼睛挤到额头，脸颊下垂，大部分面部被一张褶皱的嘴占据。它的腹部肿胀且近乎透明，带着病态的天鹅绒色调。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'spitter zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s spews out concentrated glob of blood acid!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s喷出一团浓缩的血酸！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "crawling zombie"
msgid_plural "crawling zombies"
msgstr[0] "爬行僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crawling zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This human corpse drags itself along slowly with its arms.  Its legs are damaged beyond repair.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这具人类尸体用双臂缓慢拖行自身。它的腿部受损严重，无法修复。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "skeletal brute"
msgid_plural "skeletal brutes"
msgstr[0] "骸骨蛮兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skeletal brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Distorted outgrowths of calcified bone plates cover this zombie's rotten skin.  Joints and cracks around its body ooze with black goo.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"扭曲的钙化骨板增生覆盖了这只僵尸的腐烂皮肤。身体关节和裂缝处渗出黑色粘液。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "skeletal juggernaut"
msgid_plural "skeletal juggernauts"
msgstr[0] "骸骨巨像"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skeletal juggernaut'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This hideous golem of plated bones and misshapen flesh drags its heavy, pointed limbs behind it like an unwanted burden.  Formerly soft and vulnerable, bones grew around its form to protect it - only, they kept growing.  And growing.  And growing.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这具由板状骨骼和畸形血肉构成的可怕魔像，拖着沉重尖锐的肢体，如同背负着不受欢迎的负担。原本柔软脆弱的骨骼在其形态周围生长以作保护——只是，它们不断生长。再生长。继续生长。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "survivor zombie"
msgid_plural "survivor zombies"
msgstr[0] "幸存者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'survivor zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Still wearing the tattered remnants of improvised armor and weaponry, it is plain to see that this zombie was once a survivor like you.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"它仍穿着临时装甲和武器的破烂残余，显而易见，这只僵尸曾是一位像你一样的幸存者。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "slavering biter"
msgid_plural "slavering biters"
msgstr[0] "垂涎啃咬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'slavering biter'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A distorted and swollen human body.  Its jaws have elongated into a crocodile like snout, dripping with foul smelling saliva.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具扭曲肿胀的人体。它的下颌伸长成鳄鱼般的口鼻，滴落着恶臭的唾液。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "brainless zombie"
msgid_plural "brainless zombies"
msgstr[0] "无脑僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'brainless zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A zombie like any other, except that its features and skull have been devastated.  It's unclear what caused the damage, but between the scraps of flesh you can see that its face and brain are gone, though its ears are intact.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只与其他无异的僵尸，只是它的面部特征和头骨已被摧毁。不清楚是什么造成了这种损伤，但在碎肉之间，你可以看到它的脸和大脑已消失，尽管耳朵完好无损。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "listener zombie"
msgid_plural "listener zombies"
msgstr[0] "聆听者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'listener zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"The head of this zombie was once obviously destroyed, the gaps in its scraps of face now filling with a peculiar gray goo.  Human ears hang from the sides, enormous and unsettling.  Thin slits at the front suggest it may be able to see.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只僵尸的头部显然曾被摧毁，面部碎片的缝隙中现在填满了一种奇特的灰色粘液。人类耳朵挂在两侧，巨大而令人不安。前端的细缝暗示它可能具备视觉能力。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "skull zombie"
msgid_plural "skull zombies"
msgstr[0] "骷髅僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skull zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This creature's head is a hideous gray skull, formed of human bone fragments and some sort of goo.  Jagged teeth are visible as the thing works its jaw and disturbingly human, lidless eyes stare at you from their sockets.  The thing's fleshy ears are four sizes too large and droop under their own weight.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个怪物的头颅是一个骇人的灰色骷髅，由人类骨片和某种粘稠物构成。当它活动下巴时，参差不齐的牙齿清晰可见，而无眼睑、令人不安的人形眼睛从眼窝中凝视着你。它那肉质的耳朵大了四号，因自身重量而下垂。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
#: Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "zombie brute"
msgid_plural "zombie brutes"
msgstr[0] "僵尸蛮兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Its entire body bulges with distended muscles and swollen, festering wounds.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"它的整个身体因膨胀的肌肉和肿胀、溃烂的伤口而隆起。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie wrestler"
msgid_plural "zombie wrestlers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸摔跤手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie wrestler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A slab of festering muscle the size of a well-toned bodybuilder.  Seems eager to strangle the life from you.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一块溃烂的肌肉板，大小堪比体格健美的健美运动员。似乎渴望将你扼杀。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie nightstalker"
msgid_plural "zombie nightstalkers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸夜行者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie nightstalker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Somehow this brute hides in the dark like some kind of boogeyman.  Very agile for such a large zombie.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"不知何故，这个蛮兵像某种怪物一样隐藏在黑暗中。对于如此庞大的僵尸来说，它非常敏捷。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "grappler zombie"
msgid_plural "grappler zombies"
msgstr[0] "擒抱僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grappler zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"An undead humanoid, its elongated arms drag along the ground as it moves.  It looks to almost have a hunch from the swollen back and shoulder muscles tearing though its skin.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一个不死的人形生物，移动时其细长的手臂拖在地上。由于肿胀的背部和肩部肌肉撕裂皮肤，它看起来几乎有些驼背。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie hollow"
msgid_plural "zombie hollows"
msgstr[0] "空心僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie hollow'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Black hollow eyes survey the surroundings as the zombie stretches and bends in ways that whoever the original body belonged to never could.  The only thing that seems solid, on this flexible black-veined body, is the rows of sharp black teeth.  You get the feeling that the only human thing remaining is the skin, worn as one would wear clothes.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"当僵尸以原主身体从未有过的方式伸展和弯曲时，空洞的黑眼睛审视着周围。在这个灵活、布满黑色血管的身体上，唯一看起来坚固的东西是那几排锋利的黑牙。你感觉唯一剩下的人类特征就是皮肤，像穿衣服一样被披在身上。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie hulk"
msgid_plural "zombie hulks"
msgstr[0] "僵尸巨怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie hulk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A human body now swollen to the size of six men, with arms as wide as a trash can.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具人类躯体现已肿胀到六个人的大小，手臂宽如垃圾桶。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "feral hunter"
msgid_plural "feral hunters"
msgstr[0] "野性猎手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'feral hunter'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This once-human body is barely recognizable, scrambling about on all fours, its nails and teeth both sharpened into dangerous looking spikes.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这具曾经的人类躯体几乎无法辨认，它四肢着地爬行，指甲和牙齿都被磨尖成危险的尖刺状。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie snapper"
msgid_plural "zombie snappers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸咬噬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie snapper'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"With a crocodile-like snout and rows of protruding teeth, this swimwear-clad zombie lurks in the water.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"长着鳄鱼般的口鼻和几排突出的牙齿，这个身穿泳装的僵尸潜伏在水中。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie master"
msgid_plural "zombie masters"
msgstr[0] "僵尸大师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie master'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Once human, its features have tightened, its lips pulled back into an unnatural grin, revealing rows of blackened teeth beneath its large, piercing eyes.  It stands tall and its movements are fluid and tightly controlled.  A feeling of danger permeates the air around it, and the light that falls on it seems somehow harsher and more glaring.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"它曾是人类，如今面部特征紧绷，嘴唇向后咧成一个不自然的狞笑，露出大而锐利的眼睛下方几排发黑的牙齿。它站得笔直，动作流畅且控制严密。一种危险感弥漫在它周围的空气中，落在它身上的光线似乎也变得更加刺眼和耀眼。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie necromancer"
msgid_plural "zombie necromancers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸死灵法师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie necromancer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A twisted mockery of the human form, emaciated, with jet black skin and glowing red eyes.  It is somehow painful to look at, awakening fears deep within your psyche, and even the air around it seems more sinister, somehow darker and more dangerous\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一个对人类形态的扭曲嘲弄，骨瘦如柴，皮肤漆黑，眼睛发出红光。看着它莫名令人痛苦，唤醒了你内心深处最深的恐惧，甚至它周围的空气也似乎更加险恶，更加黑暗和危险。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了其大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "feral predator"
msgid_plural "feral predators"
msgstr[0] "野性掠食者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'feral predator'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"With its joints in odd places and angles, this humanoid creature prowls across the landscape with surprising speed.  Its teeth and arms are sharpened into fine points, and black ooze seeps out from cuts between its muscles\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个人形生物的关节位于怪异的位置和角度，以惊人的速度在土地上潜行。它的牙齿和手臂被磨成锋利的尖刺，黑色的黏液从肌肉间的切口渗出。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "screecher zombie"
msgid_plural "screecher zombies"
msgstr[0] "尖啸僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'screecher zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A thin corpse, its chest is swollen in what appears to be preparation.  A thick black ooze drips from its open mouth.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具瘦削的尸体，其胸部肿胀，仿佛在准备着什么。浓稠的黑色黏液从它张开的嘴中滴落。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "thorny shambler"
msgid_plural "thorny shamblers"
msgstr[0] "荆棘蹒跚者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'thorny shambler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A shambling undead humanoid, body overgrown with a tangled mass of otherworldly vegetation.  Hunched over and dragging its feet as it moves, the bramble utterly enveloping its upper half twitches and moves with a life of its own, tendrils tipped with a paralytic sting.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一个蹒跚的不死人形生物，身体上长满了纠缠的异界植被。它弯腰驼背，拖着脚步移动，完全包裹上半身的荆棘丛抽搐着，仿佛有自己的生命，末梢带有麻痹性毒刺的卷须。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "smoker zombie"
msgid_plural "smoker zombies"
msgstr[0] "烟雾僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'smoker zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A blackened and twisted naked human body, strips of flesh hang from its body, and it emits a constant haze of thick, velvety smoke.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具发黑扭曲的赤裸人体，肉条从身上垂下，不断散发出浓密如天鹅绒般的烟雾。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "anklebiter"
msgid_plural "anklebiters"
msgstr[0] "咬踝者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anklebiter'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This horrifying little mutated wretch looks to have once been a child, but its massive gaping jaws are now far more suggestive of a predatory beast.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个可怕的小型突变可怜虫看起来曾是个孩子，但它那巨大张开的颌骨现在更像捕食野兽。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie child"
msgid_plural "zombie children"
msgstr[0] "僵尸孩童"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie child', 'str_pl': 'zombie children'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"It was only a child, and little is different about it now aside from the hungry look in its eyes.  You'd be hard pressed to not feel like you were killing an actual child by putting it down.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"它只是个孩子，现在除了眼中饥饿的神情外变化不大。你很难不觉得杀死它就像在杀害一个真正的孩子。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "creepy crawler"
msgid_plural "creepy crawlers"
msgstr[0] "爬行怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'creepy crawler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"What was once a child is now a mutant beast with blackened skin and massive eyes.  This abomination's vile form makes mockery of its human origin.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"曾经的孩子现在成了皮肤发黑、眼睛巨大的突变野兽。这个可憎生物的邪恶形态嘲弄着它的人类起源。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "shriekling"
msgid_plural "shrieklings"
msgstr[0] "尖啸幼体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shriekling'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This heavily mutated child zombie twitches and flails its limbs in painful looking spasms as it runs about.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个严重突变的孩子僵尸在四处奔跑时，肢体抽搐挥舞，看起来痛苦地痉挛着。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "snotgobbler"
msgid_plural "snotgobblers"
msgstr[0] "鼻涕吞噬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snotgobbler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This swollen, gooey looking mutant child looks bad, even for a zombie.  Maybe that's why it seems to want a hug so badly.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个肿胀、黏糊糊的突变孩子看起来很糟，即使对僵尸来说也是如此。也许这就是它如此渴望拥抱的原因。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "sproglodyte"
msgid_plural "sproglodytes"
msgstr[0] "洞穴幼怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sproglodyte'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This crouching child-mutant's face is dominated by a pair of huge black eyes and its fingertips end in sharp claws.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个蹲伏的孩子突变体脸上有一对巨大的黑眼睛，指尖是锋利的爪子。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "howling waif"
msgid_plural "howling waifs"
msgstr[0] "嚎叫流浪儿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'howling waif'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Undeath has not been kind to the children of the apocalypse.  This one is little more than a reanimated membrane of skin stretched across tiny brittle bones.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"末日之子并未从死亡中获得仁慈。这具躯体不过是一层复活的皮肤薄膜，覆盖在细小脆弱的骨骼上。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "shocker brute"
msgid_plural "shocker brutes"
msgstr[0] "电击蛮兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shocker brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A huge beast covered in visible scarring from what you can only guess was 'research'.  Being near it, you can hear a slight humming, like that of an electrical transformer.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一头巨大的野兽，身上布满可见的疤痕，你只能猜测那是“研究”所致。靠近它时，你能听到轻微的嗡嗡声，如同电力变压器一般。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "shocker zombie"
msgid_plural "shocker zombies"
msgstr[0] "电击僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shocker zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A human body with pale blue flesh, crackling with electrical energy.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具苍白蓝色肉体的人体，周身噼啪作响着电能。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "incandescent husk"
msgid_plural "incandescent husks"
msgstr[0] "白炽空壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'incandescent husk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This once-human is visible only as a glowing white silhouette that you have to squint to see, cloaked in a crackling field of lightning that pulses like a beating heart.  It walks slowly and deliberately, the thunderstorm surrounding it eagerly jumping to anything conductive within its grasp.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这个曾经的人类仅呈现为一个发光的白色轮廓，你必须眯眼才能看清，它笼罩在一层噼啪作响的闪电场中，如同搏动的心脏般脉动。它缓慢而刻意地行走，环绕的雷暴急切地扑向其掌控范围内的任何导电物体。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zapper zombie"
msgid_plural "zapper zombies"
msgstr[0] "电击者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zapper zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A very pale dead body with the worst case of static hair you have ever seen.  Sometimes, you can see sparks of electricity around it.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具非常苍白的尸体，有着你见过最严重的静电头发。有时，你能看到它周围闪烁的电火花。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie scientist"
msgid_plural "zombie scientists"
msgstr[0] "僵尸科学家"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie scientist'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Apart from the jet-black eyes, this zombie looks less decomposed and inhuman than most.  Clad in a tattered lab coat, it seems to have a glimmer of awareness - not a human awareness, but something more sinister.  As you watch it, its movements look almost marionette-like.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"除了漆黑的双眼，这只僵尸看起来比大多数同类腐烂程度更低，也更不像非人生物。它身披一件破烂的实验袍，似乎闪烁着一丝意识——并非人类的意识，而是某种更险恶的东西。当你观察它时，它的动作几乎像木偶一般。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "boomer"
msgid_plural "boomers"
msgstr[0] "爆破者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'boomer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A rotund human body, bloated beyond belief and layered in rolls of fat.  It emits a horrible odor, and a putrid pink sludge dribbles from its mouth.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具圆胖的人体，肿胀得难以置信，层层脂肪堆积。它散发出可怕的气味，腐臭的粉色黏液从嘴角滴落。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "huge boomer"
msgid_plural "huge boomers"
msgstr[0] "巨型爆破者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'huge boomer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This boomer, normally swollen and ready to burst, has strengthened and solidified.  The bile dribbling from its mouth also appears to have changed.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只爆破者通常肿胀欲裂，现已强化并固化。从它口中滴落的胆汁似乎也发生了变化。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "gasoline zombie"
msgid_plural "gasoline zombies"
msgstr[0] "汽油僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gasoline zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A huge bloated zombie that appears to have fed upon gasoline; fumes and flames escape from its mouth and fuel leaks from its waddling form.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只巨大的肿胀僵尸，似乎以汽油为食；烟雾和火焰从它口中逸出，燃料从其蹒跚的躯体中泄漏。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "bloated zombie"
msgid_plural "bloated zombies"
msgstr[0] "肿胀僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloated zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"With its gray skin swollen to near rupture with putrid gas, this cyst covered zombie looks like it could violently burst under the slightest of disturbances.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"它的灰色皮肤因腐臭气体肿胀至近乎破裂，这只囊肿覆盖的僵尸看起来在轻微扰动下就可能猛烈爆裂。\n"
"薄膜状的血管覆盖了它大部分表面，持续搏动着。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie soldier"
msgid_plural "zombie soldiers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸士兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie soldier'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Once a soldier, it is dressed head to toe in combat gear and carries itself rather steadily for a zombie.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"曾是一名士兵，它从头到脚穿着战斗装备，作为僵尸而言行动相当稳健。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "black-ops zombie"
msgid_plural "black-ops zombies"
msgstr[0] "黑色行动僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'black-ops zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This soldier zombie's skin radiates a sort of shadowy smoke that obscures its outline, making its camouflage even harder to see against the background.  In the darkness it would be nigh invisible.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只士兵僵尸的皮肤散发出一种阴影般的烟雾，模糊了其轮廓，使其伪装在背景中更难被察觉。在黑暗中它几乎隐形。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "hunter-killer zombie"
msgid_plural "hunter-killer zombies"
msgstr[0] "猎杀者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hunter-killer zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Fragments of visible uniform hint that this monstrosity was once a soldier.  Anything human is invisible, hidden inside a sheath of living shadow.  It moves with preternatural fluidity and grace.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"可见的制服碎片暗示这头怪物曾是一名士兵。任何人性的部分都已消失，隐藏在一层活体阴影之中。它以超自然的流畅与优雅移动。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "acid-sniper zombie"
msgid_plural "acid-sniper zombies"
msgstr[0] "酸液狙击僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'acid-sniper zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This staggering soldier wears a burnt gasmask, now fused to its face.  Through the melted, bile-encrusted ruination of the mask comes some sort of hardened fleshy proboscis, with steaming corrosive fluid leaking from the end.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只蹒跚的士兵戴着一个烧焦的防毒面具，现已与脸部融合。透过融化、覆满胆汁的面具残骸，伸出一根硬化肉质的喙状物，末端渗漏着蒸腾的腐蚀性液体。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "acid-support zombie"
msgid_plural "acid-support zombies"
msgstr[0] "酸液支援僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'acid-support zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This zombie wears what appears to have once been a soldier's uniform and armor, now a series of cracked and melted plates that have fused to its skin and thickened hide.  Its face and arms blister with strange mutated tubes that pulse and drip with acid.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只僵尸穿着看似曾是士兵制服与盔甲的衣物，如今已变成一系列破裂融化的板甲，与其皮肤和增厚的表皮融合。其面部和手臂布满搏动并滴落酸液的怪异突变管状物。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "Kevlar zombie"
msgid_plural "Kevlar zombies"
msgstr[0] "凯夫拉僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kevlar zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This zombie was once wearing some kind of uniform with heavy, bulletproof materials sewn in.  At this point it's impossible to tell what kind of uniform it was: the monster's skin has grown over the fabric, splitting and tearing it to shreds, turning the remaining Kevlar and other bits of armor material into part of its hide.  Its hands, similarly, have fused into large leathery cudgels.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只僵尸曾穿着某种缝有厚重防弹材料的制服。如今已无法辨认原貌：怪物的皮肤已覆盖织物，将其撕裂成碎片，使剩余的凯夫拉和其他装甲材料成为其表皮的一部分。其双手同样融合成了大型革质棍棒。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "Kevlar hulk"
msgid_plural "Kevlar hulks"
msgstr[0] "凯夫拉巨怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Kevlar hulk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This zombie was once wearing some kind of now long-shredded uniform with heavy, bulletproof materials sewn in.  It has grown into a hulking, leatherbacked beast, its mutated skin taking on a strange texture similar to the Kevlar bits embedded in it.  Its arms have twisted into enormous clubs of misshapen bone that it drags on the ground behind it.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只僵尸曾穿着某种现已破碎的制服，缝有厚重防弹材料。它已长成一头庞大、背覆革皮的野兽，其突变皮肤呈现出与嵌入的凯夫拉碎片相似的怪异质地。其双臂扭曲成畸形的巨大骨棒，拖曳在地面上。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie military pilot"
msgid_plural "zombie military pilots"
msgstr[0] "僵尸军事飞行员"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie military pilot'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Once a pilot, it is dressed in basic military fatigues, aviator sunglasses, and a sturdy looking helmet.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"曾是一名飞行员，它穿着基本军服、飞行员墨镜和一顶看起来坚固的头盔。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie bio-operator"
msgid_plural "zombie bio-operators"
msgstr[0] "僵尸生物操作员"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie bio-operator'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This armored and augmented soldier's bionics crackle with energy.  Worse, it appears to remember its training.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这名装甲强化士兵的仿生装置闪烁着能量。更糟的是，它似乎还记得所受的训练。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "veteran survivor zombie"
msgid_plural "veteran survivor zombies"
msgstr[0] "老兵幸存者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'veteran survivor zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This zombie once was a survivor like you, and a pretty good one at that.  Unfortunately they didn't make it, despite the custom-made, heavy armor pieces they wear and the gear that they are still lugging around.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只僵尸曾像你一样是幸存者，而且相当出色。不幸的是，尽管穿着定制重型护甲并仍携带装备，他们未能幸免。\n"
"其大部分表面覆盖着搏动的膜状血管。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "acidic zombie"
msgid_plural "acidic zombies"
msgstr[0] "酸性僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'acidic zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A sickly-looking dead one.  Its skin looks especially thin, with a sticky, yellow fluid flowing through the clearly visible veins.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具病态的死者。它的皮肤看起来异常薄，粘稠的黄色液体在清晰可见的血管中流动。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "corrosive zombie"
msgid_plural "corrosive zombies"
msgstr[0] "腐蚀僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corrosive zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This body has swollen to immense proportions, but still manages to hold itself together with semi-congealed acid all over its bloated body.  It clumsily moves around, but attacks with a large reserve of acid.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这具躯体已肿胀到巨大比例，但全身覆盖的半凝固酸液仍将其勉强维系在一起。它笨拙地移动着，却能利用体内储备的大量酸液进行攻击。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "The corrosive zombie spits a glob of blood acid!"
msgstr "腐蚀僵尸吐出一团血酸！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "wretched puker"
msgid_plural "wretched pukers"
msgstr[0] "可憎呕吐者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wretched puker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A degenerate corpse, shambling as it walks.  Several junks and waste materials have unified into its skin and wounds around it reeks in black goo.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一具退化的尸体，行走时步履蹒跚。几块垃圾和废料已融入它的皮肤，周围的伤口散发着黑色黏液的恶臭。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombie dog"
msgid_plural "zombie dogs"
msgstr[0] "僵尸犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie dog'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"The deformed, animated corpse of a canine, a sinewy beast which can easily outpace its two-legged friends.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只犬类的畸形活化尸体，这头筋肉发达的野兽能轻易超越它的双足朋友们。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "skeletal dog"
msgid_plural "skeletal dogs"
msgstr[0] "骸骨犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skeletal dog'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This once-canine has shed all of its skin, revealing a carapace of fused bones and ribs.  Devoid entirely of flesh, this walking suit of bone seems to be controlled by a net of veins and sinews which pulse with glistening black goo.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只曾经的犬类已褪去所有皮肤，露出融合骨骼与肋骨构成的外壳。完全失去血肉后，这具行走的骨甲似乎由脉动着闪亮黑色黏液的血管与肌腱网络所控制。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "Z-9"
msgid_plural "Z-9s"
msgstr[0] "Z-9"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Z-9'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A zombified version of one of the German shepherd dogs used in law enforcement.  Its deformed body is encased in a protective Kevlar harness.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只执法用德国牧羊犬的僵尸化版本。它畸形的躯体包裹在防护性凯夫拉背带中。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "rot-weiler"
msgid_plural "rot-weilers"
msgstr[0] "腐罗威犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rot-weiler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"Acrid smell accompanies this corpse of canine.  Its whole body is covered in chains of pulsing cysts and slime-dribbling ulcers.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"刺鼻气味伴随着这具犬类尸体。它的全身覆盖着搏动的囊肿链与滴落黏液的溃疡。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "grim howler"
msgid_plural "grim howlers"
msgstr[0] "阴森嚎叫者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grim howler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A zombified wolf.  Its mouth oozes with a black substance, coating the vicious-looking white fangs.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只僵尸化的狼。它的嘴巴渗出黑色物质，覆盖了那狰狞的白色尖牙。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombear"
msgid_plural "zombears"
msgstr[0] "僵尸熊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombear'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This black bear's eyes ooze with dark, oily fluid, and its flesh is torn and scarred.  It shuffles as it walks.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只黑熊的眼睛渗出暗色油状液体，它的皮肉撕裂且布满疤痕。行走时它拖着脚步蹒跚移动。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "festering boar"
msgid_plural "festering boars"
msgstr[0] "溃烂野猪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'festering boar'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"A zombified omnivore descended from the wild boar.  Now it's got black goo all over it, instead of mud.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只源自野猪的僵尸化杂食动物。如今它全身覆盖着黑色黏液，而非泥浆。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它的大部分表面，这些血管在有节奏地搏动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "zombeaver"
msgid_plural "zombeavers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸海狸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombeaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This wall-eyed beast has a large wound on its side, and ribs with some flesh on them are seen through it.  The most prominent feature of this abomination is large incisors in its ominously open mouth, strange black goo is oozing out of it.  Seems like it isn't interested in trees anymore and is looking for some warm flesh to feed.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这只斜眼野兽身侧有一道巨大的伤口，透过伤口可见肋骨上残留着些许血肉。这头可憎怪物最显著的特征是它那张不祥张开的嘴中巨大的门齿，从中渗出诡异的黑色粘液。看来它已对树木失去兴趣，转而寻找温热的血肉为食。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而起伏。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "antlered horror"
msgid_plural "antlered horrors"
msgstr[0] "鹿角恐怖兽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'antlered horror'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"This formerly-majestic moose has succumbed to the infection which is killing the world.  Shiny green blowflies swarm the vast suppurated patches of purulent flesh where its skin has sloughed away, and its remaining fur is black and matted with necrotic discharge.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"这头昔日雄伟的驼鹿已屈服于正在毁灭世界的感染。闪亮的绿色丽蝇群聚在它皮肤脱落处大片化脓的腐肉上，剩余的皮毛呈黑色，被坏死分泌物黏结成块。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而起伏。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid "decayed pouncer"
msgid_plural "decayed pouncers"
msgstr[0] "腐化扑击者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'decayed pouncer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Flesh_undead.json
msgid ""
"An otherwise normal-looking cougar, except that its hind legs are swollen, and its eyes bulge with black goo.\n"
"Membranous veins cover most of its surface that pulsates in constant beats."
msgstr ""
"一只外表看似正常的山狮，只是其后腿肿胀，眼睛因黑色粘液而凸出。\n"
"膜状血管覆盖了它大部分表面，随着持续的搏动而起伏。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fleshling'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid ""
"A tiny slab of meat that moves by either hopping or slithering through the "
"ground. Attracted to flesh."
msgstr "一小块通过跳跃或在地面蠕动移动的肉片。会被血肉吸引。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'fleshling'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'small flesh blob'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh blob'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'big flesh blob'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s devours %3$s...</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s吞噬了%3$s...</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid "small flesh blob"
msgid_plural "small flesh blobs"
msgstr[0] "小型血肉团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small flesh blob'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid ""
"A small slab of meat that's larger than a basketball. Will try to devour "
"anything nearby."
msgstr "一块比篮球稍大的肉片。会试图吞噬附近的任何东西。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid "flesh blob"
msgid_plural "flesh blobs"
msgstr[0] "血肉团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh blob'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid ""
"A slab of meat that's larger than a dog. Will try to devour anything nearby."
msgstr "一块比狗还大的肉片。会试图吞噬附近的任何东西。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid "big flesh blob"
msgid_plural "big flesh blobs"
msgstr[0] "大型血肉团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'big flesh blob'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid ""
"A big slab of meat that's larger than a human. Will try to devour anything "
"nearby."
msgstr "一块比人类还大的巨型肉片。会试图吞噬附近的任何东西。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid "flesh mound"
msgid_plural "flesh mounds"
msgstr[0] "血肉丘"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh mound'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
msgid ""
"A humongous conglomeration of rotten flesh, as large as a moose. Its body "
"has swollen and stretched out, and seem to slowly deteriorate, but its "
"endless hunger still is apparent to its motion."
msgstr "一团如驼鹿般庞大的腐烂血肉聚合体。它的身体肿胀拉伸，似乎正在缓慢崩解，但其无尽的饥饿仍能从它的动作中明显看出。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh mound'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Crimson Horrors\Fleshlings.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s devours %3$s...</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s吞噬了%3$s...</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "saddler broodmother"
msgid_plural "saddler broodmothers"
msgstr[0] "鞍背虫育母"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saddler broodmother'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"Fiendish giant saddler with numerous green, hairy spindly legs covering its "
"entire bottom. Underneath them produces a heavy, eerie sound, much like from"
" the baby saddlers not given birth... yet."
msgstr ""
"邪恶的巨型鞍背虫，整个下半身覆盖着无数绿色、多毛的细长腿。其下方发出沉重而诡异的声响，很像那些尚未诞生的幼年鞍背虫发出的声音...目前还未出生。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'saddler broodmother'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>The saddler broodmother gave birth to baby saddlers!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>鞍背虫育母产下了幼年鞍背虫！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "baby saddler"
msgid_plural "baby saddlers"
msgstr[0] "幼体鞍背虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'baby saddler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A rancid, immature saddler, stumbling frequently as its feeble limbs twitch "
"without command."
msgstr "一只腐臭、未成熟的鞍背虫，虚弱的肢体不受控制地抽搐，导致它频繁踉跄。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'baby saddler'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "<color_magenta>The bady saddler twitches...</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>幼体鞍背虫抽搐着...</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saddler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"An alien-like insect, distinct to its several spindly limbs, beany eyes and "
"skinny hide. Its humped head and large bottom slit suggests its organ's not "
"functioning in animalistic way."
msgstr "一种类似外星昆虫的生物，以其数条细长的肢体、豆状的眼睛和瘦削的外皮为特征。它隆起的头部和巨大的底部裂口表明其器官并非以动物性的方式运作。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saddler brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"Saddler with a huge hump and limbs twice the size its predecessor. Unlike "
"others, its primal instinct is more on ferocious onslaughts."
msgstr "鞍背虫，拥有巨大的驼峰和比前代大一倍的肢体。与其他同类不同，它的原始本能更倾向于凶猛的攻击。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "saddler scout"
msgid_plural "saddler scouts"
msgstr[0] "鞍背虫斥候"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'saddler scout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A thin, slender saddler, drooling foul substance as it travel in its sharp "
"limbs. Frail, it excels in sprinting all the way to its desired target."
msgstr "一只瘦削、纤细的鞍背虫，移动时用其锋利的肢体滴下恶臭的液体。虽然脆弱，但它擅长一路冲刺至其目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "infected saddler"
msgid_plural "infected saddlers"
msgstr[0] "感染鞍背虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infected saddler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"Once human, now a stout vessel succumbed to the parasitic fiend. Its entire "
"head has been 'eaten' under the slit of the saddler, while its hands has "
"turned into viscious sharp claws. It moans in agony, and somewhat deep, "
"inaudible mumbling voice is heard while near it."
msgstr ""
"曾经是人类，现在是一个屈服于寄生恶魔的强壮容器。它的整个头部已被鞍背虫的裂口“吞噬”，而双手则变成了恶毒的利爪。它在痛苦中呻吟，靠近时能听到某种深沉、难以听清的咕哝声。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "infected brute"
msgid_plural "infected brutes"
msgstr[0] "感染蛮兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infected brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A humped human fallen under control to the brutal saddler. Its defiled claws"
" reek with blood, hinting its sudden alteration caused minor drawbacks "
"visible to its thickened skin layers."
msgstr "一个被残暴鞍背虫控制、驼背的人类。它被玷污的利爪散发着血腥味，暗示其突然的变异导致了可见的轻微缺陷，体现在其增厚的皮肤层上。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "infected scout"
msgid_plural "infected scouts"
msgstr[0] "感染斥候"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'infected scout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"An infected human with a slender and seemingly flexible body, with claws "
"curved into horrifying pairs of sharp slashers. Yet deadly, its alteration "
"causes the host's flesh and internal organs to become dense, which made its "
"vital extremeties much fragile."
msgstr "一个被感染的人类，身体纤细且看似柔韧，爪子弯曲成恐怖成对的锋利切割器。虽然致命，但变异导致宿主的肉体和内脏变得致密，使其要害部位更加脆弱。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "zombie saddler"
msgid_plural "zombie saddlers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸鞍背虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie saddler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A corpse with large, skinny head dripping in black goo and a pair of "
"intimidating sharp claws. Unknown to how the saddler managed to manipulate "
"this undead's mind, but surely its senses are duller and the body "
"alterations were amplified unlike the living's."
msgstr ""
"一具尸体，拥有巨大、瘦削的头颅，滴着黑色粘液，以及一对令人生畏的利爪。不知鞍背虫如何操控这具亡灵的思维，但可以肯定它的感官更迟钝，身体变异也比活体更显著。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A rugged zombie with a large saddler head and hands turned into bony claws. "
"Its body can take a number of blows, but the stiffness of its skin made its "
"movements look like it was crippled."
msgstr "一个粗糙的僵尸，长着巨大的鞍背虫头部，双手变成了骨爪。它的身体能承受多次打击，但皮肤的僵硬使其动作看起来像是跛足。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "zombie scout"
msgid_plural "zombie scouts"
msgstr[0] "僵尸斥候"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie scout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A slim corpse with a slender saddler as its head and arms twice the average "
"length, tipped with viciously sharp claws. Despite its thin, feeble body, "
"it's nimble motion outpaces most of its target."
msgstr "一具纤细的尸体，以细长的鞍背虫作为头部，手臂长度是平均水平的两倍，末端是恶毒的利爪。尽管身体瘦弱，但其敏捷的动作能超越大多数目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "headless zombie"
msgid_plural "headless zombies"
msgstr[0] "无头僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'headless zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A headless walking corpse. Its hands has turned into sharp claws, with its "
"wound pulsating with black goo."
msgstr "一具无头的行走尸体。它的双手变成了锋利的爪子，伤口处随着黑色粘液脉动。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "headless brute"
msgid_plural "headless brutes"
msgstr[0] "无头蛮兵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'headless brute'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A stout, headless body. It has a very thick skin and an overgrown set of "
"nails, depicting this corpse has once mutated."
msgstr "一具粗壮的无头躯体。它有着极厚的皮肤和过度生长的指甲，表明这具尸体曾发生过变异。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid "headless scout"
msgid_plural "headless scouts"
msgstr[0] "无头斥候"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'headless scout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Saddler.json
msgid ""
"A headless zombie with a slender body and long, sharp-clawed arms, seemingly"
" a product of mutation."
msgstr "一只无头僵尸，身体细长，手臂长而带有利爪，似乎是变异的产物。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid "noxious eater"
msgid_plural "noxious eaters"
msgstr[0] "剧毒食尸者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'noxious eater'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid ""
"A large, flabby worm with hundreds of dreadful teeth aligned inside its "
"little mouth. It has grown fond of eating necrotic flesh."
msgstr "一条巨大而松软的蠕虫，其小嘴内排列着数百颗可怕的牙齿。它已变得嗜食坏死肉体。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid "grave digger"
msgid_plural "grave diggers"
msgstr[0] "掘墓者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grave digger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid ""
"A huge, crimson worm with its thick skin formed like a tough rubber. Under "
"its quad-interloping fangs hinder thousands of ravenous teeth."
msgstr "一条巨大的深红色蠕虫，其厚皮如坚韧橡胶般构成。在它四颗交错獠牙之下，隐藏着数千颗贪婪的牙齿。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'grave digger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s ravages!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s 肆虐！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid "writhing horror"
msgid_plural "writhing horrors"
msgstr[0] "扭曲恐魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'writhing horror'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid ""
"A massive worm with hundreds of tentacle outgrowths twisting incessantly "
"from its sickly pale red skin. Under its flabby head reveals a row of "
"sinister teeth, deeply accompanied by compact tendrils."
msgstr "一条巨大的蠕虫，其病态苍白的红色皮肤上不断扭曲着数百条触手状增生。在它松软的头部下方，露出一排阴森的牙齿，周围紧密环绕着紧凑的触须。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'writhing horror'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s ravages as it aims at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 肆虐，并瞄准了 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid "sinister maw"
msgid_plural "sinister maws"
msgstr[0] "邪恶魔口"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sinister maw'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid ""
"A colossal worm, mysterious to its origin. Its glistening white surface "
"depicts its sly nature, but once it attempts to feast on its prey, its maw "
"can deliver strands of web-like flesh with an inner mouth allowing to "
"consume from a distance."
msgstr "一条庞大的蠕虫，其起源神秘。它闪亮的白色外表显露出狡猾的本性，但一旦试图捕食猎物，其巨口能喷射出蛛网般的肉丝，并通过内部口腔实现远程吞噬。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'sinister maw'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s ravages, then points its orifice at %3$s...</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 肆虐，随后将其口器指向 %3$s……</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid "wormonger"
msgid_plural "wormongers"
msgstr[0] "蠕虫暴君"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wormonger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
msgid ""
"A catastrophic worm as wide as a car, with the rest of its body hidden "
"underneath. Its overconsumption of dead bodies must've caused it to suffer "
"from further mutations."
msgstr "一条灾难性的蠕虫，宽如汽车，其余身体部分隐藏在地下。它过度摄食尸体，必定导致了进一步的变异。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'wormonger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\Worms.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_magenta>%1$s ravages as it emits an ear-piercing screech!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s 肆虐，并发出刺耳的尖啸！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\ZombieParasiteWorms.json
msgid "parasitic swarm"
msgid_plural "parasitic swarms"
msgstr[0] "寄生虫群"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'parasitic swarm'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Insects\ZombieParasiteWorms.json
msgid ""
"Slithering parasite worms of unknown origin, still coated in fresh zombie "
"blood."
msgstr "来历不明的滑行寄生蠕虫，身上仍覆盖着新鲜的僵尸血液。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid "carrion"
msgid_plural "carrions"
msgstr[0] "腐肉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carrion'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid ""
"Erratic and frightful, a bane from an otherworldly ruined dimension. It has "
"no distinct appearance and is heavily malformed, but noted as a lump of "
"necrotic skin."
msgstr "行为无常且令人恐惧，是来自异界废墟维度的灾厄。它没有明确的外形，严重畸形，被描述为一团坏死的皮肤。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid "carrion dismantler"
msgid_plural "carrion dismantlers"
msgstr[0] "腐肉拆解者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carrion dismantler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid ""
"Overgrown bone blades adore this carrion's limbs, sharp as it glimmers in "
"the light. Stronger and tougher, but it is sluggish than the normal ones."
msgstr "过度生长的骨刃装饰着这具腐肉的肢体，在光线下闪烁，锋利无比。它更强壮坚韧，但比普通个体更为迟缓。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid "carrion orifice"
msgid_plural "carrion orifices"
msgstr[0] "腐肉孔洞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carrion orifice'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid ""
"Quite larger than the others, this carrion has large, gaping holes scattered"
" around, pressumably the mouths as they are lined with rotten bony "
"materials."
msgstr "体型远大于其他同类，这具腐肉身上散布着巨大的裂口，推测为嘴巴，边缘排列着腐烂的骨质材料。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid "carrion overseer"
msgid_plural "carrion overseers"
msgstr[0] "腐肉监工"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'carrion overseer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Carrion.json
msgid ""
"With much more dreadful appearance and a loathsome huge body attached with "
"various assortment of limbs and appendages, this carrion must be the pack "
"leader. Its skin undulates in bloodshot tint as its predominant \"eye\" "
"eagerly skims through the vicinity."
msgstr ""
"外观更为骇人，庞大的身躯上附着各式各样的肢体与附属物，这具腐肉想必是族群的首领。它的皮肤在血红色调中起伏，其主导的“眼睛”急切地扫视着周围。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector"
msgid_plural "vectors"
msgstr[0] "矢量"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid ""
"A briskly, nearly 10-feet tall light blue-ish plant with luminating broad "
"leaves and errant stripes in its stem and branches, twitching wildly as it "
"moves. Feeble yet pleasant to the sight, dust particles enshroud the "
"creature that twinkles like a starry night sky."
msgstr ""
"一种敏捷的、近10英尺高的浅蓝色植物，拥有发光的宽大叶片，茎干与枝条上带有不规则的条纹，移动时剧烈扭动。它看似脆弱却赏心悦目，尘埃颗粒笼罩着这生物，闪烁如星空。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vector'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vector sprout'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vector spore'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vector bloom'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vector tree'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s blooms a vector haze!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s绽放出矢量迷雾！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector sprout"
msgid_plural "vector sprouts"
msgstr[0] "矢量新芽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector sprout'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid ""
"A dangling vector sprout, as tall as a person. Immature, it reeks in "
"twinkling particles from its leaves and thick branches."
msgstr "一株悬垂的矢量新芽，与人同高。尚未成熟，其叶片与粗枝散发出闪烁的微粒。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector sprig"
msgid_plural "vector sprigs"
msgstr[0] "矢量小枝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector sprig'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "A writhing dark blue-ish stem, with leaves the size of a fist."
msgstr "一根扭动的深蓝色茎干，叶片如拳头大小。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector spore"
msgid_plural "vector spores"
msgstr[0] "矢量孢子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector spore'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "A compact dust, blown and floats gently in the air."
msgstr "一团致密的尘埃，被吹起后在空气中轻柔飘浮。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector bloom"
msgid_plural "vector blooms"
msgstr[0] "矢量花"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector bloom'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid ""
"A vector with unique floral blooms by the end of its branches. Undulates "
"occasionally, it sends a finer dust into the surroundings."
msgstr "一株矢量，其枝条末端绽放着独特的花朵。它偶尔起伏，向周围释放更细腻的尘埃。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid "vector stinger"
msgid_plural "vector stingers"
msgstr[0] "矢量刺针"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector stinger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid ""
"Long thorns cover this vector's bark. A thinner with lesser foliage, like a "
"dead bush, but much quicker and seeps in blue-ish thick saps."
msgstr "长满尖刺覆盖着此载体的树皮。它枝叶稀疏，形似枯灌木，但移动更为迅捷，并能渗出蓝稠的汁液。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vector tree'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\Vector.json
msgid ""
"An elderly vector, much higher and larger than a regular oak tree. Nearly "
"immobile, strands of dense vines cover its thick bark and whenever the wind "
"howls, its starlight dusts spread even further."
msgstr "一株年迈的载体，远比普通橡树高大。几乎无法移动，浓密的藤蔓缠绕其粗厚树皮，每当狂风呼啸，其星尘便会飘散得更远。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Unknown'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\___.json
msgid ""
"A ripple of time and space, transparent and emits a gravitational force "
"field, like that of a black hole's surrounding. Unidentified, it leaves you "
"uncomfortable as if it is a threat or not."
msgstr "一道时空涟漪，透明且散发引力场，宛如黑洞周遭。身份不明，它让你感到不安，仿佛是一种威胁。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Unknown\___.json
msgid "???"
msgid_plural "???"
msgstr[0] "？？？"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid "skittering weaver"
msgid_plural "skittering weavers"
msgstr[0] "疾行编织者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'skittering weaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid ""
"A mutated creature, the size of a cat with hybrid appearance of a tick and a"
" beetle. Its forelimbs form a pair of oddly curved needles, tipped with a "
"vented gap and saliva-drooling mandibles."
msgstr "一种突变生物，体型如猫，兼具蜱虫与甲虫的混合特征。其前肢形成一对奇曲的针状结构，尖端带有通风孔与垂涎的下颚。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'skittering weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'replenishing weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s flees from %3$s!</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>Then %1$s hastily injects its needle!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s逃离了%3$s！</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>随后%1$s匆忙注射了它的针管！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid "replenishing weaver"
msgid_plural "replenishing weavers"
msgstr[0] "补给编织者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'replenishing weaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid ""
"A vile insect, protected beneath a membranous shelling. Shares similar "
"traits to its predecessor, except the fact that it has grown larger in size."
msgstr "一种邪恶昆虫，受膜质外壳保护。与其前身特征相似，但体型更为庞大。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid "plague weaver"
msgid_plural "plague weavers"
msgstr[0] "瘟疫编织者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plague weaver'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#: Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
msgid ""
"A heavily mutated insect, with several spindly limbs stretching outwards "
"from its membranous beetle shell. Deformed in every angle, a distinctive "
"proboscis drips an intoxicating substance."
msgstr "一种严重突变的昆虫，数条细长肢体从其膜质甲壳向外伸展。全身扭曲变形，独特的口器滴落着致幻物质。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'plague weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Amalgams.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s flees from %3$s!</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>Then %1$s hastily injects its proboscis!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_light_red>%1$s逃离了%3$s！</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>随后%1$s匆忙注射了它的口器！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid "kaxix"
msgid_plural "kaxixs"
msgstr[0] "卡克西斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'kaxix'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, with its hands ruptured into a scythe and a head "
"similar to eels. It is wearing an experimental suit, denoting a state of "
"progress."
msgstr "一种人形生物，双手裂变为镰刀状，头部类似鳗鱼。身着实验服，标志着进化状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, with its hands ruptured into a scythe and a head "
"similar to eels. Clad in special suit of armor, it has an encrusted \"SS\" "
"symbol on its chest."
msgstr "一种人形生物，双手裂变为镰刀状，头部类似鳗鱼。身披特殊盔甲，胸前镶嵌着“SS”符号。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid "axxuros"
msgid_plural "axxuross"
msgstr[0] "阿克苏罗斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'axxuros'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, partially suffering in necrotic shelling. Both of its "
"arm merged and developed numerous bony spikes between them. It is wearing an"
" experimental suit, denoting a state of progress."
msgstr "一种人形生物，部分躯体受坏死外壳侵蚀。双臂融合并在其间生出大量骨刺。身着实验服，标志着进化状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, partially suffering in necrotic shelling. Both of its "
"arm merged and developed numerous bony spikes between them. Clad in special "
"suit of armor, it has an encrusted \"SS\" symbol on its chest."
msgstr "一种人形生物，部分躯体受坏死外壳侵蚀。双臂融合并在其间生出大量骨刺。身披特殊盔甲，胸前镶嵌着“SS”符号。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid "exios"
msgid_plural "exioss"
msgstr[0] "埃克西奥斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'exios'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, with head and tail featuring a canine appearance. One "
"of its hand altered into heaps of tentacle tipped with awkward bony blades. "
"It is wearing an experimental suit, denoting a state of progress."
msgstr "一种人形生物，头尾呈现犬类特征。一手变异为成堆触须，末端连接笨拙的骨刃。身着实验服，标志着进化状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A humanoid creature, with head and tail featuring a canine appearance. One "
"of its hand altered into heaps of tentacle tipped with awkward bony blades. "
"Clad in special suit of armor, it has an encrusted \"SS\" symbol on its "
"chest."
msgstr "一种人形生物，头尾呈现犬类特征。一手变异为成堆触须，末端连接笨拙的骨刃。身披特殊盔甲，胸前镶嵌着“SS”符号。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid "drexx"
msgid_plural "drexxs"
msgstr[0] "drexx"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'drexx'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A large humanoid creature, with its hand morphed like that of a hammer. Made"
" out of solidified bone, its momentum could do more than what is expected. "
"It is wearing an experimental suit, denoting a state of progress."
msgstr "一个大型人形生物，其手部变形为锤状。由凝固的骨骼构成，其冲击力远超预期。它穿着一套实验服，标志着进展状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A large humanoid creature, with its hand morphed like that of a hammer. Made"
" out of solidified bone, its momentum could do more than what is expected. "
"Clad in special suit of armor, it has an encrusted \"SS\" symbol on its "
"chest."
msgstr "一个大型人形生物，其手部变形为锤状。由凝固的骨骼构成，其冲击力远超预期。身披特殊盔甲，胸前镶嵌着“SS”符号。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid "epixo"
msgid_plural "epixos"
msgstr[0] "epixo"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'epixo'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A gigantic, morbidly deformed creature, vaguely a humanoid in appearance. "
"with its bulging muscles and disastrous nature, its seeks wrath to the "
"living. It is wearing a special experimental suit, denoting a state of "
"progress."
msgstr "一个巨大、病态畸变的生物，外观隐约呈人形。凭借其隆起的肌肉和灾难性的本质，它向生者寻求愤怒。它穿着一套特殊的实验服，标志着进展状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+BOWs.json
msgid ""
"A gigantic, morbidly deformed creature, vaguely a humanoid in appearance. "
"with its bulging muscles and disastrous nature, its seeks wrath to the "
"living. Clad in special suit of armor, it has an encrusted \"SS\" symbol on "
"its chest."
msgstr "一个巨大、病态畸变的生物，外观隐约呈人形。凭借其隆起的肌肉和灾难性的本质，它向生者寻求愤怒。身披特殊盔甲，胸前镶嵌着“SS”符号。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "seeker"
msgid_plural "seekers"
msgstr[0] "seeker"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'seeker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid ""
"Alluring large skin in shape of a starfish and mouth slits nibbles near "
"every tip. Its abdomen is infused with gigantic lizard eye, eager to seek "
"its prey."
msgstr "诱人的大型皮肤呈海星形状，每个尖端附近都有嘴缝轻咬。其腹部融合了一只巨大的蜥蜴眼睛，渴望寻找猎物。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "flora"
msgid_plural "floras"
msgstr[0] "flora"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flora'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid ""
"A human body with its head mutated and deformed into a flowery petal mouth. "
"It shows hundreds of teeth and a centered eye whenever it opens."
msgstr "一具人体，其头部变异并畸形为花瓣状嘴巴。每当张开时，会露出数百颗牙齿和一只位于中央的眼睛。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "distorted crawler"
msgid_plural "distorted crawlers"
msgstr[0] "distorted crawler"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'distorted crawler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid ""
"A twisted body with various attachments of human anatomy, resulting into a "
"nightmarish agile crawler. Its head ruptured into a horrid mouth and a "
"fiendish eye inside, constantly opens and close to survey its vicinity."
msgstr ""
"一个扭曲的身体，附着着各种人体解剖结构，形成了一个噩梦般敏捷的爬行者。其头部破裂成一张可怕的嘴巴和一只内部的恶魔之眼，不断开合以侦察周围环境。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "chomper"
msgid_plural "chompers"
msgstr[0] "chomper"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chomper'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid ""
"Headless humanoid monster, with its rib ruptured into a torsal eyed mouth. "
"The arms are gone, yet it is a threat not to be misjudged."
msgstr "无头的人形怪物，其肋骨破裂形成一个躯干上的眼睛嘴巴。手臂已消失，但它仍是一个不容小觑的威胁。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "squirtler"
msgid_plural "squirtlers"
msgstr[0] "squirtler"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'squirtler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid ""
"Attached to the terrain, this irregular patch of large, pale skin features a"
" swollen, bulbous mouth, oozing in greenish liquid."
msgstr "附着在地形上，这片不规则的大块苍白皮肤有一个肿胀的球状嘴巴，渗出绿色液体。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Failed.json
msgid "The squirtler spew a stream of acid!"
msgstr "squirtler喷出一股酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "nautilus"
msgid_plural "nautiluss"
msgstr[0] "nautilus"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nautilus'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A morbidly large zombie heavily mutated from long exposure to irradiated "
"waters, which altered most of its body parts into something, like that of a "
"mollusk. Sluggish, yet full of surprises."
msgstr "一个病态巨大的僵尸，因长期暴露在辐射水域而严重突变，使其大部分身体部位变得类似软体动物。行动迟缓，却充满惊喜。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'nautilus'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s submerges and generates a seismic wave towards "
"%3$s</color>!"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s潜入水中并向%3$s生成一道地震波</color>！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "nautilus torpedo"
msgid_plural "nautilus torpedos"
msgstr[0] "鹦鹉螺鱼雷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nautilus torpedo'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A squidling, or some sort of maggot, but with tentacles. Tiny, feeble and "
"short-lived, it seeks a lively host on its ways to attach to."
msgstr "一只小鱿鱼，或某种蛆虫，但长有触手。它体型微小、虚弱且短命，在途中寻找活跃的宿主以附着其上。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'nautilus torpedo'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s latches onto %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 紧紧抓住了 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "dissonant screamer"
msgid_plural "dissonant screamers"
msgstr[0] "不谐尖啸者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dissonant screamer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A skinny tall zombie with swollen mouth and elongated jaws, seeping with "
"black ooze. Its harsh, high-pitched voice makes it suprisingly dangerous."
msgstr "一只瘦高的僵尸，嘴巴肿胀，下巴拉长，渗出黑色黏液。它刺耳尖锐的嗓音使其出奇地危险。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "jolt"
msgid_plural "jolts"
msgstr[0] "电震尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jolt'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A pale corpse, obscure to its appearance. Flowing through its body is an "
"immensive electric current."
msgstr "一具苍白的尸体，外貌模糊不清。其体内流淌着强大的电流。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "bolt"
msgid_plural "bolts"
msgstr[0] "电球"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bolt'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "An electric crackling ball, floating freely in the air."
msgstr "一个噼啪作响的电球，自由地漂浮在空中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bolt'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "A large, electric crackling ball, floating freely in the air."
msgstr "一个巨大的、噼啪作响的电球，自由地漂浮在空中。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"red eyes."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，其油亮的红眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s ruptures into an ichorus!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s 爆裂成了一只脓浆怪！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "ichorus"
msgid_plural "ichoruss"
msgstr[0] "脓浆怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ichorus'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Heaps of greenish flesh has replaced the head under its undulating bulbous "
"torso. Slow and is heavily hampered, yet it opposes a big threat for its "
"corrosive bodily fluids."
msgstr "成堆的绿色肉块取代了其波动球状躯干下的头部。它行动缓慢且严重受阻，但其腐蚀性体液构成了巨大威胁。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s ruptures into a psyrus!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s 爆裂成了一只狂噬者！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "psyrus"
msgid_plural "psyruss"
msgstr[0] "狂噬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'psyrus'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A large, wickedly vile corpse, with writhing tendrils under its foul mouth. "
"Veins glow brighter as its raging desire for flesh sets it ablazed."
msgstr "一具巨大、邪恶可憎的尸体，其污秽的嘴巴下扭动着触须。对血肉的狂暴渴望使其血管发出更亮的光芒，如同燃烧一般。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "uruxis"
msgid_plural "uruxiss"
msgstr[0] "乌鲁克西斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'uruxis'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Shrouded in ominous black mist, this corpse's horrid visage strikes fear to "
"the minds of the conscious ones."
msgstr "笼罩在不祥的黑雾中，这具尸体的恐怖面容给清醒者的心灵带来恐惧。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'uruxis'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s curses the surrounding area as it enshrouds itself in "
"shadows!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 诅咒了周围区域，同时将自己笼罩在阴影之中！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "clinger"
msgid_plural "clingers"
msgstr[0] "攀附者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'clinger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Covered in foul stench, this ambiguously dreadful 4-legged creature dangles "
"as it moves, grasping and gnawing anything in its surroundings."
msgstr "这只形态模糊、令人畏惧的四足生物浑身散发着恶臭，移动时摇摇晃晃，会抓咬周围的一切。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'clinger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s lunges at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s扑向了%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "nocturne"
msgid_plural "nocturnes"
msgstr[0] "夜曲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nocturne'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Concealed in otherworldly shadows, this vicious corpse brings terror to its "
"unfortunate prey. Sets of razor nails glow faintly in the darkness, and "
"baneful eyes affixed to the void."
msgstr "这具凶残的尸体隐匿于异界阴影之中，为不幸的猎物带来恐惧。成对的利爪在黑暗中微微发光，恶毒的眼睛凝视着虚空。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'nocturne'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>Errant shadows emerges from %1$s as they perform an "
"onslaught!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>游荡的阴影从%1$s中涌现，并发起猛攻！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "nix"
msgid_plural "nixs"
msgstr[0] "虚无"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nix'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A hollow corpse, suffering from severe deterioration of flesh that made it "
"appear completely skeletal. Its ghastly visage is uncomfortable to the "
"sight, and being near it is the worst than most."
msgstr "一具空洞的尸体，因肉体严重腐烂而显得完全骨架化。其可怖的面容令人不适，靠近它比大多数情况更糟。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "fleshmonger"
msgid_plural "fleshmongers"
msgstr[0] "嗜肉者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fleshmonger'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A gigantic mound of putrid flesh, with assortments of limbs and writhing "
"tendrils reemerging back and forth. Dark, oozing pus constantly erupts in "
"its swollen body."
msgstr "一座巨大的腐肉堆，各种肢体和蠕动的触须来回涌现。深色、渗出的脓液不断从其肿胀的身体中喷发。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'fleshmonger'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s pierces the nearby monsters!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s刺穿了附近的怪物！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "gorepit"
msgid_plural "gorepits"
msgstr[0] "血污坑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gorepit'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"An eerie pit composed mostly of decaying flesh, with a distinctive huge gap "
"revealing thousands of bones and other organic materials aligned in its "
"wall. Thick, sinewy webbing supports a central bulbous orb that beats at a "
"steady rate."
msgstr ""
"一个诡异的坑穴，主要由腐烂的肉体构成，其巨大的裂口显露出内壁排列着数千块骨头和其他有机物质。厚实的筋状网支撑着一个中央球状体，以稳定的节奏搏动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'gorepit'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_red>You feel the ground shaking as it originates from %1$s!</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>%1$s sends a defeaning screech!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_red>你感到地面震动，源自%1$s！</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>%1$s发出震耳欲聋的尖啸！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "giant tendril"
msgid_plural "giant tendrils"
msgstr[0] "巨型触须"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant tendril'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A stout, meandering tendril, consisting of flesh and bones. Its vein glows "
"in sync with the orb."
msgstr "一条粗壮、蜿蜒的触须，由血肉和骨骼构成。其血管与球体同步发光。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'giant tendril'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s slams at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s猛击%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "corrupted devourer"
msgid_plural "corrupted devourers"
msgstr[0] "腐化吞噬者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corrupted devourer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A colossal, humanoid corpse, distinct to its seemingly volatile, torsal "
"lump, a headless top and a set of arm biters with swollen eyes united into "
"them. Drools corrupted acid, its great desire for flesh has sent its hunger "
"beyond limitations, thus reaping and feasting upon its fellow undeads has "
"became its norm."
msgstr ""
"一具巨大的人形尸体，其显著特征是一个看似不稳定的躯干肿块、无头的顶部以及一对长有肿胀眼睛的臂状啃咬器。它流着腐化酸液，对血肉的强烈渴望使其饥饿感超越极限，因此收割并吞食同类亡灵已成为常态。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'corrupted devourer'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s's sight locks onto %3$s...</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s的视线锁定了%3$s……</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "flesilisk"
msgid_plural "flesilisks"
msgstr[0] "肉蜥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesilisk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A massive conglomeration of thick, gangrenous flesh, forming a snake-like "
"figurine with its head resembling a dragon. Terrifyingly disastrous, its "
"entire body is covered in bony scales and lies under it are spikes of "
"similar material. Yet its great lack of intuitive perception causes it to "
"easily become enraged by the time it senses a prey."
msgstr ""
"一团巨大的、由厚实坏疽血肉构成的聚合体，形似蛇状，头部宛如恶龙。其恐怖至极，全身覆盖着骨鳞，下方布满同材质的尖刺。然而，它极度缺乏直觉感知，导致在察觉到猎物时极易暴怒。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesilisk'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s's rage intensifies as it glares at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s怒视着%3$s，怒火愈发炽烈！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "akin"
msgid_plural "akins"
msgstr[0] "同源体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'akin'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A grotesquely baneful corpse, resonating pure dread in the air as it eagerly"
" sways along its path. Visceral tendrils slither freely in its vicinity, "
"acting like guides in sensing the unfortunate host."
msgstr "一具怪诞而恶毒的尸体，在空气中回荡着纯粹的恐惧，急切地沿着路径摇摆。内脏触须在其周围自由蠕动，如同向导般感知着不幸的宿主。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'akin'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s's visceral tendril undulates while it is attached to "
"%3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s的内脏触须附着在%3$s身上，不断波动！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "equinox"
msgid_plural "equinoxs"
msgstr[0] "昼夜体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'equinox'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"An overwhelming mass of flesh resembling a brain, constantly excreting "
"vaporized poison gas originating from its protruding shroom-like outgrowths."
" Large, hollow gaps reveal nothing but shady gloom. However, when observed "
"closely, harsh screeches are heard indistinctly."
msgstr ""
"一团形似大脑的庞大肉块，不断从其突出的蘑菇状增生组织中排出汽化的毒气。巨大而空洞的缝隙中只有阴暗的幽影。然而，仔细观察时，能隐约听到刺耳的尖啸声。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'equinox'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>Twisted abominations starts to crawl out of %1$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>扭曲的憎恶生物开始从%1$s中爬出！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "necros"
msgid_plural "necross"
msgstr[0] "死骸体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'necros'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A mutated lump of necrotic flesh, horribly twisted into a spindy creature. "
"Its limbs are tipped with a neurotoxic substance that reacts for almost "
"instantly upon contact with the air. "
msgstr "一团变异的坏死肉块，可怕地扭曲成细长的生物。其肢体末端带有神经毒素物质，一旦接触空气几乎瞬间反应。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "necros impaler"
msgid_plural "necros impalers"
msgstr[0] "死骸穿刺者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'necros impaler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A mutated lump of necrotic flesh, horribly twisted into a spindy creature. A"
" long, thick strand of contorted tissue protrudes from a gap you can only "
"tell is its mouth. By the end of its lasher secretes a concentrated toxin."
msgstr "一团变异的坏死肉块，可怕地扭曲成细长的生物。一根长而粗的扭曲组织从仅能辨识为嘴部的缝隙中伸出。其鞭状末梢分泌着浓缩毒素。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "necros slicer"
msgid_plural "necros slicers"
msgstr[0] "死骸切割者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'necros slicer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A mutated lump of necrotic flesh, horribly twisted into a spindy creature. "
"Its forelimbs form a pair of scythed blades, and its extra appendages writhe"
" without a pause as they drip neurotoxins from its tip."
msgstr "一团变异的坏死肉块，可怕地扭曲成细长的生物。其前肢形成一对镰刀状刀刃，额外的附肢不停扭动，从尖端滴落神经毒素。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "necros pollutant"
msgid_plural "necros pollutants"
msgstr[0] "死骸污染者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'necros pollutant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A mutated lump of necrotic flesh, horribly twisted into a spindy creature. "
"Larger in its size, its excessive production of toxin has become its source "
"in emitting a condensed fog, yet a cause to its unstable body."
msgstr "一团变异的坏死肉块，可怕地扭曲成细长的生物。体型更为庞大，其过量产生的毒素成为释放浓缩雾气的源头，却也导致其身体不稳定。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "relinquished zombie"
msgid_plural "relinquished zombies"
msgstr[0] "弃绝僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'relinquished zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A diluted zombie, staggering as its wicked eyes only show a vigorious "
"expression to whom it looks at. One can easily take its life, but something "
"inhumane lingers around this rotting vessel..."
msgstr "一只稀释化的僵尸，蹒跚而行，其邪恶的眼睛只对注视对象展现出强烈的表情。人们可以轻易夺其性命，但这具腐烂躯壳中却萦绕着某种非人的气息……"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "resolute zombie"
msgid_plural "resolute zombies"
msgstr[0] "决意僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'resolute zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"While in the verge of death, life has sprung again to bring wrath "
"relentlessly. A skinless, brutal zombie constantly growing visible to its "
"masculine body slowly gaining mass. Obscure to the limit of its growth, onee"
" must execute this impending disaster."
msgstr ""
"濒死之际，生命再度迸发，带来无情的怒火。一只无皮、野蛮的僵尸，其雄壮身躯不断增长，质量逐渐累积。其成长极限难以估量，必须铲除这场迫在眉睫的灾难。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "stray zombie"
msgid_plural "stray zombies"
msgstr[0] "游荡僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A zombie, nothing more special about it. Yet it is just a normal day walker,"
" it is considered a lone wolf, shuffling its way into nothingness."
msgstr "一只僵尸，并无特别之处。它只是寻常的昼行尸，被视为独行侠，蹒跚步入虚无。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A zombie, nothing more special about it. Yet it is just a normal day walker,"
" it is considered a lone wolf, shuffling its way into nothingness. Vines are"
" visible under its dress, but it doesn't seem to benefit nor bother the zed."
msgstr "一只僵尸，并无特别之处。它只是寻常的昼行尸，被视为独行侠，蹒跚步入虚无。其衣物下可见藤蔓，但这似乎既未助益也未困扰这只僵尸。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Heaps of vibrant vines and stems cover this stray's body, holding its rotten"
" flesh in place. Nearly immobile, it is a peculiar sight to behold for one's"
" curious mind."
msgstr "茂盛的藤蔓与茎秆覆盖着这只游荡者的躯体，将其腐肉固定。近乎无法移动，对好奇之心而言是一幅奇特的景象。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Bound to the nature's grace, this stray has become one with the plant. Skin "
"hardened like a bark, vines guides the undead's clumsy movements, but in "
"search for flesh, the stray manipulates."
msgstr "受自然恩典束缚，这只游荡者已与植物融为一体。皮肤硬化如树皮，藤蔓引导着不死者笨拙的动作，但在寻觅血肉时，游荡者却能自如操控。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'stray zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s slashes %3$s with its razor sharp leaves!"
msgstr "%1$s用其锋利的叶片劈砍%3$s！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"In its age, leaves, vines, everything, has grown larger and tougher. A "
"stray, ascendant of nature, has cultivated some beautiful, yet strange "
"blooming flowers."
msgstr "随着岁月流逝，叶片、藤蔓，一切皆变得更大更坚韧。一只游荡者，自然的升华者，培育出美丽而奇异的绽放花朵。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'stray zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"%1$s strikes the ground, then a wild outgrowth of vines and branches erupts "
"under %3$s!"
msgstr "%1$s猛击地面，随后藤蔓与枝条的狂野生发在%3$s脚下爆发！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"In every step it takes, befalls seducing spores from its coveted flowers. "
"This almighty stray of nature, has succesfully ascended into a frightful "
"vine beast."
msgstr "它每踏一步，珍稀花朵便洒下诱人的孢子。这只自然界的全能游荡者，已成功升华为骇人的藤蔓巨兽。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'stray zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"%1$s strikes the ground, then a wild outgrowth of vines and branches erupts under %3$s!\n"
"Triffids burst out of it too!"
msgstr ""
"%1$s猛击地面，随后藤蔓与枝条的狂野生发在%3$s脚下爆发！\n"
"三裂植物也从中破土而出！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "triffid"
msgid_plural "triffids"
msgstr[0] "三裂植物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'triffid'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A creeping animate plant, growing as tall as a moose.  It has a single bark-"
"covered stalk supporting a flowery head with a paralyzing sting concealed "
"within."
msgstr "一种匍匐的活化植物，生长如驼鹿般高大。它有一根覆满树皮的主茎，支撑着花状头部，内藏麻痹毒刺。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A zombie, nothing more special about it. Yet it is just a normal day walker,"
" it is considered a lone wolf, shuffling its way into nothingness. A green-"
"ish vein by its arm faintly glows."
msgstr "一只僵尸，并无特别之处。它只是寻常的昼行尸，被视为独行侠，蹒跚步入虚无。其手臂上一道泛绿的血管微微发光。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Seeps in green-ish fluid, this stray - shambling as it walks - is defiled by"
" its own blood."
msgstr "渗出泛绿的液体，这只游荡者——步履蹒跚——被自身的血液所玷污。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"Prolonged for too long from its acidic blood caused its skin to sag, but it "
"has seemingly adapted to take hold of the harsh substance."
msgstr "长期受酸性血液侵蚀导致皮肤松弛，但它似乎已适应并掌控了这严酷的物质。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"An acidic stray, now manipulates its own fluid to its will. Reeks in acid "
"trail, it is determined to spread the corrosion along its aimless wandering."
msgstr "一只酸性游荡者，如今能随心操纵自身液体。散发着酸蚀痕迹，它决心在无目的的游荡中传播腐蚀。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'stray zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s sends a large amount of concentrated acid to %3$s!"
msgstr "%1$s向%3$s喷射大量浓缩酸液！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'stray zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"This corrosive stray, has finally ascended and developed an even and "
"produces more lethal bodily fluid from aging, visibly gurgling on its "
"bloated green-ish veins under the elastic, transparent skin."
msgstr "这只腐蚀性游荡者，终得升华，因年岁增长而分泌出更致命的体液，其弹性透明的皮肤下，肿胀的泛绿血管中可见液体汩汩涌动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'stray zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s sends a massive glob of acid above %3$s, then explodes violently!"
msgstr "%1$s向%3$s上方投掷一大团酸液，随后猛烈爆炸！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "fleshknot"
msgid_plural "fleshknots"
msgstr[0] "血肉结"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fleshknot'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A giant amalgamation of flesh is cemented firmly into the floor and ceiling,"
" preceded by the horrid miasma of putrid stenches emanating from the growth."
" The majority of the flesh binds into a central, knot-like growth that "
"rhythmically pumps and undulates; similar to that of the heart of a horribly"
" mutated creature."
msgstr ""
"一团巨大的血肉融合体被牢牢固定在地板和天花板之间，其生长处散发出的腐臭瘴气令人作呕。大部分血肉缠绕成一个中央结状结构，有节奏地搏动起伏，宛如一只严重变异生物的心脏。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "The fleshknot sends out a cluster of tendrils!"
msgstr "血肉结释放出一簇触须！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "The fleshknot thrusts its tentacles!"
msgstr "血肉结猛刺其触手！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid "goreknot"
msgid_plural "goreknots"
msgstr[0] "血污结"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'goreknot'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\+Misc.json
msgid ""
"A giant amalgamation of flesh is cemented firmly into the floor and ceiling,"
" preceded by the horrid miasma of putrid stenches emanating from the growth."
" A somewhat humanoid figure is molded in the center of this abomination "
"accompanied by large, membranous tentacles."
msgstr ""
"一团巨大的血肉融合体被牢牢固定在地板和天花板之间，其生长处散发出的腐臭瘴气令人作呕。在这畸形体的中心塑造出一个类人形轮廓，周围环绕着巨大的膜状触手。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh, with several tube-like orifices scattered "
"around its surface. Its body seeps with blood acid."
msgstr "一堆聚合的血肉，表面散布着数个管状孔口。其身体不断渗出血液酸液。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "flesh heap (blade)"
msgid_plural "flesh heap (blade)s"
msgstr[0] "血肉堆（刃核）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap (blade)'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh infused with blade core. Its body is filled "
"with hundreds of bone outgrowths, and new ones keep on growing. And growing."
msgstr "一堆注入了刃核的聚合血肉。其体内充满数百根骨刺增生，且新的骨刺仍在不断生长。持续生长。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh heap (blade)'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s undulates</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 起伏波动</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "flesh heap (tendril)"
msgid_plural "flesh heap (tendril)s"
msgstr[0] "血肉堆（触须核）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap (tendril)'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh infused with tendril core. Several tendril "
"outgrowths writhe incessantly around its surface, varying in density scales."
msgstr "一堆注入了触须核的聚合血肉。数条触须增生在其表面不停扭动，密度规模各异。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh heap (tendril)'}"'s spell
#. "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s writhes!</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 剧烈扭动！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "flesh heap (mouthswell)"
msgid_plural "flesh heap (mouthswell)s"
msgstr[0] "血肉堆（口胀核）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap (mouthswell)'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh infused with mouthswell core. Jawed mouths "
"form a choir of shrieks and screeches as it blankly skims through its "
"surroundings."
msgstr "一堆注入了口胀核的聚合血肉。带颚的嘴巴组成一阵尖叫与嘶鸣的合唱，同时它茫然地扫视着周围环境。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'flesh heap (mouthswell)'}"'s spell
#. "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_light_red>%1$s shakes erratically...</color>"
msgstr "<color_light_red>%1$s 不规则地颤动...</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "flesh heap (unifier)"
msgid_plural "flesh heap (unifier)s"
msgstr[0] "血肉堆（统合核）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'flesh heap (unifier)'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh infused with unifier core. Its swollen "
"portions throb in a constant beat, accompanied by numerous wriggly "
"tentacles."
msgstr "一堆注入了统合核的聚合血肉。其肿胀部分以恒定节律搏动，伴随着无数蠕动的触手。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid "ravager flesh heap"
msgid_plural "ravager flesh heaps"
msgstr[0] "掠夺者血肉堆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ravager flesh heap'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
msgid ""
"A heap of conglomerated flesh infused with several cores. This hybrid turret"
" takes advantage on the tendril's relentless assaults and the blade's "
"formation of sharp bone outgrowths."
msgstr "一堆注入了多个核心的聚合血肉。这种混合炮塔利用了触须的 relentless 攻击和刃核形成的锋利骨刺增生。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'ravager flesh heap'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\BO Turrets.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s writhes wildly!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 剧烈地扭动着！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid "blade zombie"
msgid_plural "blade zombies"
msgstr[0] "刀锋僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blade zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid ""
"A normal corpse, with one of its arms mutated into a bone blade. Its not "
"that sharp to slice a skin, but enough to leave a bruise."
msgstr "一具普通的尸体，其中一只手臂变异成了骨刃。它不够锋利到能切开皮肤，但足以留下瘀伤。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blade zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid ""
"A corpse induced in rotten smell, with noticable bone sword that glimmers "
"when struck by a source of light."
msgstr "一具散发着腐烂气味的尸体，带有明显的骨剑，在光照下会闪烁微光。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blade zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid ""
"Dragging its serrated bone sword around, apparently the weight of this "
"weapon burdens the pitiful deceased."
msgstr "拖曳着它那锯齿状的骨剑，显然这件武器的重量给这可怜的死者带来了负担。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid "razor"
msgid_plural "razors"
msgstr[0] "剃刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'razor'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Bladed.json
msgid ""
"A staggering corpse, accompanied with an outright bladed arm with the length"
" similar to that of a medieval sword. Nimble and seemingly a talented "
"striker, its eyes affixed in one point, as if it takes advantage in seeking "
"the weakness of its ill-fated victim."
msgstr ""
"一具蹒跚的尸体，伴随着一只完全刀锋化的手臂，长度类似中世纪长剑。敏捷且看似天赋异禀的打击者，它的眼睛固定在一个点上，仿佛在利用这一点寻找不幸受害者的弱点。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid "charger zombie"
msgid_plural "charger zombies"
msgstr[0] "冲锋僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'charger zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid ""
"A rugged corpse with one of its arms mutated into an overgrown bulging "
"muscle, while the opposite to its other arm."
msgstr "一具粗糙的尸体，其中一只手臂变异成了过度生长的膨胀肌肉，而另一只手臂则相反。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'charger zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'vanguard'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s charges at %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s向%3$s发起冲锋！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'charger zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid ""
"A once stout zombie, now has been covered by protruding bone spikes under "
"its skin, yet its thick, mutated arm is overwhelmed by the larger ones."
msgstr "一具曾经强壮的僵尸，如今皮肤下布满了突出的骨刺，然而它那粗壮的变异手臂被更大的骨刺所压制。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'charger zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid ""
"A large corpse with its skin calcified into a layer, like a shell whose "
"purpose is to protect the underlying extremeties. It has caused its movement"
" to become stiff, and the grinding of its skin is barely heard."
msgstr "一具巨大的尸体，其皮肤钙化成一层，像是一个旨在保护下方肢体的外壳。这导致它的动作变得僵硬，皮肤的摩擦声几乎听不见。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid "vanguard"
msgid_plural "vanguards"
msgstr[0] "先锋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vanguard'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Charger.json
msgid ""
"A corpse, heavily altered into a huge mass of distorted flesh, yet still "
"retains the humanoid form. Rotten wounds lay open in its entire body, as its"
" predominant arm has overgrown excessively from prolonged mutation."
msgstr "一具尸体，被严重改造成了一大团扭曲的肉块，但仍保留着人形。腐烂的伤口遍布全身，其占主导地位的手臂因长期变异而过度生长。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "grubby zombie"
msgid_plural "grubby zombies"
msgstr[0] "蛆虫僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'grubby zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid ""
"A bloated creature seeping pus covered larvae and emitting gut wrenching "
"stenches wobbles around. \"Defiled\" would be a compliment to this grotesque"
" almost-human monstrosity that fumbles with each step, almost falling to its"
" own weight."
msgstr ""
"一只肿胀的生物，渗出覆盖着幼虫的脓液并散发出令人作呕的恶臭，摇摇晃晃地移动着。对于这个 grotesque "
"近乎人类的怪物来说，“亵渎”都算是一种恭维，它每一步都步履蹒跚，几乎要被自身的重量压倒。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "The grubby zombie spits globs of tainted goo!"
msgstr "蛆虫僵尸吐出了几团被污染的粘液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "slimy zombie"
msgid_plural "slimy zombies"
msgstr[0] "粘液僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'slimy zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid ""
"Fortified by blobs and worms infused inside its skinless body, this zombie "
"can barely walk on its feet. With slimy liquid dripping from its holes, the "
"parasites can \"swim\" faster through it."
msgstr "由注入其无皮身体的粘液团和蠕虫加固，这只僵尸几乎无法用脚行走。粘稠的液体从其孔洞中滴落，寄生虫可以借此更快地“游动”。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "The slimy zombie spits globs of tainted goo!"
msgstr "粘液僵尸吐出了几团被污染的粘液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "glut"
msgid_plural "gluts"
msgstr[0] "暴食者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glut'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid ""
"A swollen degenerate corpse, severely infested by worms that has taken all "
"over of its body, causing it to bloat excessively. These bloated portions "
"are volatile, and its sudden explosion can cause widespread explosions."
msgstr "一具肿胀的退化尸体，全身严重感染蠕虫，导致其过度膨胀。这些膨胀部位极不稳定，其突然爆炸可能引发大范围爆炸。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Grubby.json
msgid "The glut vomits globs of tainted goo!"
msgstr "肿胀者呕吐出大团受污染的粘液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
msgid "licker zombie"
msgid_plural "licker zombies"
msgstr[0] "舔食者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'licker zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
msgid ""
"A small and agile zombie with slender long tongue twitching violently, and "
"incessantly. The way it moves in four feet makes it more fearsome in a "
"chase."
msgstr "一种小型敏捷的僵尸，细长的舌头剧烈且不停地抽搐。它以四足移动的方式使其在追逐中更加可怕。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'licker zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
msgid ""
"An ever dominant licker with much more distinction to its terrific "
"appearance: its skin sheds into a fleshy physique, claws arose awkwardly and"
" its tongue grew much longer."
msgstr "一只始终占据主导地位的舔食者，其恐怖外观更为突出：皮肤蜕变为肉质体格，爪子笨拙地长出，舌头变得更长。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
msgid "lacerator"
msgid_plural "lacerators"
msgstr[0] "撕裂者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lacerator'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
msgid ""
"Covered in tender crimson flesh, this licker has reached its peak. Aside "
"from its larger, tougher body, its flexible blade-like tongue writhes in "
"search of prey."
msgstr "覆盖着柔嫩的深红色血肉，这只舔食者已达到巅峰。除了更大、更坚韧的身体外，其灵活的刀刃状舌头扭动着寻找猎物。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'lacerator'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Licker.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s stabs %3$s precisely with its tongue!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s用舌头精准地刺中了%3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid "lying body"
msgid_plural "lying bodys"
msgstr[0] "躺卧的尸体"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lying body'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid ""
"A walking swollen cocoon, seemingly made out skin. Silent moaning is heard "
"from the inside"
msgstr "一个行走的肿胀茧状物，似乎由皮肤构成。内部传来低沉的呻吟声。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid "zawk"
msgid_plural "zawks"
msgstr[0] "扎克"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zawk'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid ""
"A once humanoid distinct to its overgrown skinny wings, curved talons and a "
"beak."
msgstr "一个曾为人形的生物，以其过度生长的瘦削翅膀、弯曲的爪子和喙为特征。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid "zoth"
msgid_plural "zoths"
msgstr[0] "佐斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zoth'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid ""
"A putrid corpse that slowly hovers mid-air with its dusty wings, spreading "
"toxin in every flap it takes."
msgstr "一具腐烂的尸体，凭借其布满灰尘的翅膀缓慢悬浮在半空中，每次振翅都会散播毒素。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid "nightinwail"
msgid_plural "nightinwails"
msgstr[0] "夜嚎者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nightinwail'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid ""
"Misty black shadow that covers over a great distance. A shady winged "
"creature is barely visible from beyond it."
msgstr "覆盖大片区域的朦胧黑影。隐约可见一只带翅膀的阴暗生物藏匿其中。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'nightinwail'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>Chunks of shadow emerges from %1$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>大块阴影从%1$s中涌现！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shadow'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
msgid ""
"This is an animate shadow-looking thing. There's nothing to fear about its "
"appearance, nothing at all."
msgstr "这是一个活生生的阴影状物体。它的外表没什么好怕的，一点都没有。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'shadow'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Lying.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_magenta>%1$s explodes!</color>"
msgstr "<color_magenta>%1$s爆炸了！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid "mouthswell zombie"
msgid_plural "mouthswell zombies"
msgstr[0] "巨口肿胀僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mouthswell zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid ""
"A human body, distinct to its big, thick and morbidly deformed jaws, "
"dribbling in black ooze."
msgstr "一具人体，以其巨大、厚重且病态畸形的下颚为特征，滴落着黑色粘液。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid "bellymouth zombie"
msgid_plural "bellymouth zombies"
msgstr[0] "腹口僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bellymouth zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid ""
"Unique to its gaping mouth on its ruptured belly, this corpse poses a great "
"threat."
msgstr "其破裂腹部上张开的巨口是其独特标志，这具尸体构成了巨大威胁。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid "roundelmouth zombie"
msgid_plural "roundelmouth zombies"
msgstr[0] "轮口僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'roundelmouth zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid ""
"Gruesome sharp teeth circulate its entire mouthface, \n"
"big enough to accomodate much space, \n"
"till the eyes sink without a trace."
msgstr ""
"狰狞的利齿环绕其整个口面，\n"
"大到足以容纳广阔空间，\n"
"直至双眼沉没无迹。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid "sucker"
msgid_plural "suckers"
msgstr[0] "吸食者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sucker'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Mouth.json
msgid ""
"A large, ravenous zed, prevailing an elongated mouth viciously altered "
"similar to lamprey's. With its rough, thick skin developed to endure extreme"
" physical impacts, it focuses on gnawing at its hapless target."
msgstr "一只庞大而贪婪的僵尸，拥有类似七鳃鳗般恶意拉长的巨口。其粗糙厚实的皮肤能承受极端物理冲击，专注于啃咬无助的目标。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid "revenant"
msgid_plural "revenants"
msgstr[0] "亡魂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'revenant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid ""
"Enveloped in odd stench, this severely diluted corpse has became an overseer"
" for its fiendish undeads."
msgstr "被诡异恶臭笼罩，这具严重腐化的尸体已成为其凶恶亡灵族群的监管者。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid "forsaken revenant"
msgid_plural "forsaken revenants"
msgstr[0] "被遗弃的亡魂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'forsaken revenant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid ""
"Filled with dread and hatred, a gloomy aura enshrouds this corpse's fragile "
"body, as its eyes glare wickedly into the void."
msgstr "充满恐惧与憎恨，阴郁的气息笼罩着这具尸体脆弱的躯体，其双眼邪恶地凝视虚空。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'forsaken revenant'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s glares at %3$s submissively!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s 顺从地瞪着 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid "alluring revenant"
msgid_plural "alluring revenants"
msgstr[0] "魅惑亡魂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'alluring revenant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid ""
"Concealed beneath a thick, eerie fog, a slim, humanoid figure stands firm. "
"Mischievous, its claws drip with peculiar black goo."
msgstr "隐匿于浓厚诡异雾气之下，一具纤细人形身影屹立不动。其爪尖滴落着奇异的黑色粘液，透着恶意。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'alluring revenant'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_red>%1$s spreads its goo into the surroundings!</color>"
msgstr "<color_red>%1$s 将粘液扩散至周围环境！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'alluring revenant'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Revenant.json
msgid ""
"Concealed beneath a thick, eerie fog, a slim humanoid figure stands firm. "
"Mischievous, its claws drip with peculiar black goo."
msgstr "隐匿于浓厚诡异雾气之下，一具纤细人形身影屹立不动。其爪尖滴落着奇异的黑色粘液，透着恶意。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid "scourge zombie"
msgid_plural "scourge zombies"
msgstr[0] "灾祸僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scourge zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid ""
"A vessel of oozing pus staggering as it walks, dripping filthy liquid on its"
" path."
msgstr "一具渗出脓液的躯壳蹒跚而行，沿途滴落污秽液体。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid "zombie defiler"
msgid_plural "zombie defilers"
msgstr[0] "僵尸亵渎者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie defiler'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid ""
"A heavily deformed corpse, constantly vomiting dark ooze from its swollen "
"cheeks and an endless explosion of pus germinates the surroundings."
msgstr "一具严重畸变的尸体，不断从肿胀脸颊呕吐黑暗粘液，无尽的脓液爆发污染着周围环境。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid "lepotitsa"
msgid_plural "lepotitsas"
msgstr[0] "莱波蒂察"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lepotitsa'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
msgid ""
"A corpse of swollen ichor, as its whole body is embraced in necrotic tissue."
" Aside from its huge hump lying on its back, its skin is full of fleshy "
"holes, each emits a subtle gas."
msgstr "一具肿胀的腐尸，全身被坏死组织包裹。除了背上巨大的驼峰外，皮肤布满肉孔，每个孔洞都散发着微妙的气体。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'lepotitsa'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Scourge.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s generates a noxious, corrosive gas then sends it to "
"%3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s 生成一股有毒腐蚀性气体，并将其送往 %3$s！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Snatcher.json
msgid "snatcher zombie"
msgid_plural "snatcher zombies"
msgstr[0] "掠食者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snatcher zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Snatcher.json
msgid ""
"A writhing corpse with a unnervingly sly and cautious nature. Its pair of "
"menacingly black eyes greedily seek the living with a predominant set of "
"four protruding fangs. These inhumane teeth furiously gnash away while idle,"
" creating a maddening and reptitive \"clack\"."
msgstr ""
"一具扭动的尸体，带着令人不安的狡诈与谨慎天性。它那双威胁性的漆黑眼睛贪婪地搜寻着活物，四颗突出的獠牙尤为显眼。这些非人的牙齿在空闲时疯狂地咬合，发出令人发狂的重复“咔哒”声。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Snatcher.json
msgid "The snatcher zombie sends off its tongue!"
msgstr "掠食者僵尸射出了它的舌头！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid "spider zombie"
msgid_plural "spider zombies"
msgstr[0] "蜘蛛僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spider zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid ""
"In its fearsome appearance, this vile abomination skitters on its 4 pair of "
"limbs, as its nimble motion has gone beyond limitation."
msgstr "这邪恶的怪物以可怕的外貌用四对肢体爬行，其敏捷的动作已超越极限。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spider zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid ""
"A longer set of arms struggles this zombie to walk nor run, but now it is "
"used to jump and taking down the unexpecting target from afar."
msgstr "过长的双臂使这只僵尸难以行走或奔跑，但现在它已习惯跳跃并从远处扑倒毫无防备的目标。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spider zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid ""
"This arachnid's symmetric arms has mutated, causing its already deformed "
"nails curve into unearthly sharpened filth."
msgstr "这只蛛形怪物的对称手臂已发生变异，导致其本就畸形的指甲弯曲成非尘世的锋利污秽之物。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid "arachnia"
msgid_plural "arachnias"
msgstr[0] "蛛形怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'arachnia'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Spider.json
msgid ""
"Several protrusion of calcified materials cover this 8-legged abomination, "
"as its visage have become more sinister, revealing a set of long, dagger-"
"like mandibles along with several eyes poking around its necrotic skin. "
"Apart from its terrifying features, its movements seem to have become more "
"fluent."
msgstr ""
"这八足怪物的身上覆盖着多处钙化物质的突起，其面容变得更加险恶，露出一对长长的匕首状颚骨，以及数只眼睛从坏死的皮肤中探出。除了恐怖的特征外，它的动作似乎变得更加流畅。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "swarmer template"
msgid_plural "swarmer templates"
msgstr[0] "集群者模板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'swarmer template'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"This guy exists to ease the author's work. If you see this in-game then "
"you've cheated."
msgstr "这家伙的存在是为了减轻作者的工作量。如果你在游戏中看到这个，说明你作弊了。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "swarmer"
msgid_plural "swarmers"
msgstr[0] "集群者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"A stout humanoid body, almost in its decaying state. Unlike other swarmers, "
"something's strange on its body that attracts its \"team\"."
msgstr "一具粗壮的人形躯体，几乎处于腐烂状态。与其他集群者不同，它身上有些奇怪的东西吸引着它的“团队”。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "A normal humanoid body, almost in its decaying state."
msgstr "一具普通的人形躯体，几乎处于腐烂状态。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "hungry swarmer"
msgid_plural "hungry swarmers"
msgstr[0] "饥饿的集群者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hungry swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"A normal humanoid body, almost in its decaying state. Despite that, its "
"excitement for flesh makes it a threat."
msgstr "一具普通的人形躯体，几乎处于腐烂状态。尽管如此，它对血肉的兴奋感使其成为一种威胁。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "starving swarmer"
msgid_plural "starving swarmers"
msgstr[0] "极度饥饿的集群者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'starving swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"A normal humanoid body, almost in its decaying state. It's physique have "
"somewhat swollen."
msgstr "一具普通的人形躯体，几乎处于腐烂状态。它的体型有些肿胀。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "savage swarmer"
msgid_plural "savage swarmers"
msgstr[0] "野蛮集群者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'savage swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"Gray-ish visage in misunderstandable expression, this zombie has gone feral,"
" visible to its extreme twitching of its head. Although possesses a regular "
"body, there's something wrong in it."
msgstr "灰色面容带着难以理解的表情，这只丧尸已变得狂野，从其头部极端的抽搐可见一斑。尽管拥有常规的身体，但内部有些不对劲。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid "virulent swarmer"
msgid_plural "virulent swarmers"
msgstr[0] "剧毒集群者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'virulent swarmer'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Swarmer.json
msgid ""
"A greenish scourge with significant lust upon the living flesh. Usually "
"docile, but seeing any living thing brings this corpse to a ferocious "
"berserk, gnawing the air as it chase them down."
msgstr "一种带绿色的灾祸，对活肉有着强烈的渴望。通常温顺，但看到任何活物都会让这具尸体陷入凶猛的狂暴，一边追逐一边啃咬空气。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid "tendril zombie"
msgid_plural "tendril zombies"
msgstr[0] "触须丧尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tendril zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid ""
"A human body with two twitching tentacles and stem-like outgrowths slit "
"through the worn and tattered clothing."
msgstr "一具人体，长着两条抽搐的触手和茎状增生，从破旧褴褛的衣物中穿出。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tendril zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid ""
"A tendril zombie with its tentacle pairs thickened from further mutation."
msgstr "一只触须丧尸，其触手对因进一步突变而增厚。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tendril zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid ""
"A frail-looking corpse with raging long tentacles covering its rotten skin. "
"Its tendril pairs are tipped with a sharp bone."
msgstr "一具看似脆弱的尸体，狂怒的长触手覆盖着腐烂的皮肤。其触须对的末端带有尖锐的骨头。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid "wraith"
msgid_plural "wraiths"
msgstr[0] "怨灵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wraith'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid ""
"Dreadful outgrowths of savage tentacles accompanies this corpse's crimson "
"body, thrashing anything in its path as it moves aimlessly. Within a closer "
"look, one of its arm pulsates that burdens the body, dragging the heavily "
"mutated portion into the ground."
msgstr ""
"这具猩红身体的尸体伴随着可怕的野蛮触手增生，在漫无目的地移动时抽打路径上的一切。细看之下，它的一只手臂搏动着，拖累着身体，将高度突变的部分拖入地面。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'wraith'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s's tentacles thrashes its surroundings!</color>\n"
"<color_red>Tendrils burst out of the ground!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s的触手抽打周围环境！</color>\n"
"<color_red>触须从地面爆发！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid "tentacle"
msgid_plural "tentacles"
msgstr[0] "触手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tentacle'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Tendrils.json
msgid ""
"A fleshy tentacle, writhing violently in its surroundings. Immobile and "
"short-lived, it stretches to strike from afar."
msgstr "一条肉质的触手，在周围环境中剧烈扭动。无法移动且寿命短暂，它能伸展并从远处攻击。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid "bone"
msgid_plural "bones"
msgstr[0] "骨殖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bone'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid ""
"A large brute with several bone protrusions around its body. It's "
"surprisingly quick despite the abnormal outgrowths."
msgstr "一个巨大的蛮兽，身体周围有几处骨刺突起。尽管有异常增生，它的速度却出奇地快。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid "titan"
msgid_plural "titans"
msgstr[0] "泰坦"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'titan'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid ""
"A swollen body covered in thick exoskeleton plates and protruding bone, lays"
" under its bulging muscles."
msgstr "一个肿胀的身体，覆盖着厚厚的外骨骼板和突出的骨头，隐藏在鼓胀的肌肉之下。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'titan'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'black titan'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>%1$s blocks with both arms then sprints toward %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s用双臂格挡，然后向%3$s冲刺！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid "black titan"
msgid_plural "black titans"
msgstr[0] "黑色泰坦"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'black titan'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Titan.json
msgid ""
"Enormous muscle mass, has desaturated from high-end mutations while its "
"exoskeleton unified with the rotten tissue."
msgstr "巨大的肌肉质量，因高端突变而褪色，同时其外骨骼与腐烂组织融为一体。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Translucent.json
msgid "translucent zombie"
msgid_plural "translucent zombies"
msgstr[0] "半透明丧尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'translucent zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Translucent.json
msgid ""
"With acid covering its whole body, this raging corpse sways in every step, "
"vomiting filthy waste as its green, tinted eyes stare submissively out of "
"nowhere."
msgstr "这具狂暴的尸体全身覆盖着酸液，每一步都摇摇晃晃，呕吐着污秽的废物，它那泛着绿光的眼睛顺从地凝视着虚无。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Translucent.json
msgid "pellucid zombie"
msgid_plural "pellucid zombies"
msgstr[0] "透明僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pellucid zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Translucent.json
msgid ""
"Unrecognizable face dribbles with unfriendly liquid. This zombie's skin "
"thinned into a diversion of light, supposably an effect from producing too "
"much acid. Within a closer look, the veins are composed mostly of green-ish "
"glows."
msgstr "无法辨认的面孔滴落着不友好的液体。这只僵尸的皮肤薄到能折射光线，推测是产生过多酸液所致。近看之下，血管主要由绿色的光芒构成。"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Translucent.json
msgid "The pellucid zombie spits a concentrated glob of acid!"
msgstr "透明僵尸吐出一团浓缩的酸液！"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "unifier zombie"
msgid_plural "unifier zombies"
msgstr[0] "统一者僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'unifier zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid ""
"A severely mutated rugged corpse managed to multiply its filthy blood into a"
" thick substance, visually seen on its bloated, dark red veins. An amalgous,"
" fleshy material beats from both hands."
msgstr "一具严重突变的粗糙尸体成功将其污秽的血液增殖为浓稠物质，在其肿胀的暗红色血管上清晰可见。双手搏动着一种融合的肉质物质。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'unifier zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>A blood vessel were created under %1$s's hands!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>一条血管在%1$s的手下被创造出来！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "unity zombie"
msgid_plural "unity zombies"
msgstr[0] "团结僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'unity zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid ""
"From head down to its feet, this corpse's blood veins rapidly excretes thick"
" blood that forms an external layer, both used for aggression and "
"defensiveness. An amalgous object around its torso resonates, in every beat,"
" drips an oozing dark liquid."
msgstr ""
"从头到脚，这具尸体的血管迅速分泌出浓稠的血液，形成一层外部覆盖，既用于攻击也用于防御。其躯干周围的融合物体随着每次搏动共振，滴落出渗出的暗色液体。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'unity zombie'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>Blood vessels has emerged from %1$s's core!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>血管已从%1$s的核心涌现！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "hemofiend"
msgid_plural "hemofiends"
msgstr[0] "血魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hemofiend'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid ""
"Overgrown veins illuminated in eerie crimson filthen blood. A big, dreadful "
"corpse, merely a nightmare to its countenance and its manipulation over the "
"vital liquid."
msgstr "过度生长的血管在诡异的深红色污血中发光。一具庞大而可怕的尸体，仅其面容和对生命液体的操控就足以成为噩梦。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'hemofiend'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
#, c-format
msgid ""
"<color_red>%1$s manipulates its own blood and sends it to %3$s!</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>Several blood vessel emerges from %1$s's body!</color>"
msgstr ""
"<color_red>%1$s操控自身的血液并将其送往%3$s！</color>\n"
"<color_yellow>数条血管从%1$s的体内涌现！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "blood vessel"
msgid_plural "blood vessels"
msgstr[0] "血管"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood vessel'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid ""
"An animate substance completely made out of blood, too viscous to move in "
"limited speed. It throbs erratically."
msgstr "一种完全由血液构成的活体物质，过于粘稠，只能以有限的速度移动。它不规则地搏动着。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'blood vessel'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "<color_yellow>The blood vessel explodes!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>血管爆炸了！</color>"

#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "blood fiend"
msgid_plural "blood fiends"
msgstr[0] "血魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood fiend'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid ""
"A large, animated substance made out of thickened blood. Bloated portions of"
" its body looks volatile, and throbs at a faster pace."
msgstr "一种由浓稠血液构成的大型活体物质。其身体肿胀的部分看起来不稳定，并以更快的速度搏动。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'blood fiend'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Unifier.json
msgid "<color_yellow>The blood fiend explodes violently!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>血魔猛烈地爆炸了！</color>"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'skittering weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'replenishing weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'plague weaver'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Weaver.json
#, c-format
msgid "<color_yellow>%1$s injects %3$s!</color>"
msgstr "<color_yellow>%1$s向%3$s注射！</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Zombie.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"black eyes. It is heavily accompanied by a strong stench."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，油亮的黑眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。它周身散发着强烈的恶臭。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Zombie.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"black eyes. It is covered in irregular bone protrusions."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，油亮的黑眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。它身上覆盖着不规则的骨刺。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Zombie.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"black eyes. Several tentacle outgrowths writhe menacingly around its body."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，油亮的黑眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。数条触手状增生在其身体周围威胁性地扭动。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'zombie'}
#: .\Modification Files\Monsters\Zombies\Zombie.json
msgid ""
"A human body, swaying as it moves, an unstoppable rage visible in its oily "
"black eyes. Its hands mutated into a pair of bone blades."
msgstr "一具人体，移动时摇摇晃晃，油亮的黑眼中可见无法遏制的狂怒。它的双手变异成了一对骨刃。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 定位器全息影像"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Hologram Protection"
msgstr "全息影像防护"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hologram Protection'}
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "\"I am programmed to not engage wandering monsters.\""
msgstr "\"我的程序设定为不与游荡怪物交战。\""

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Flesh Forest Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 血肉森林定位器全息影像"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Flesh Island Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 血肉岛屿定位器全息影像"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Flesh Cave Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 血肉洞穴定位器全息影像"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Flesh City CLass 1 Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 血肉城市 1 级定位器全息影像"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Secronom Flesh City CLass 2 Locator Hologram"
msgstr "Secronom 血肉城市 2 级定位器全息影像"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Flesh Forest'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Flesh Forest"
msgstr "前往血肉森林"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to find this location for you to explore? Sure, you will just "
"need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via my "
"network system"
msgstr "要我为你定位探索地点？没问题，只需等我用网络系统查找几分钟或更短时间"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You want me to locate it now for you to explore? Sure, just tell me, you "
"will just need to wait for a couple of minutes or less for me to find it via"
" my network system"
msgstr "你想让我现在为你定位那个地点以便探索吗？当然，告诉我吧，你只需要等几分钟或更短时间，我就能通过网络系统找到它。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good luck to you!"
msgstr "祝你好运！"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Not interested in explorations of new locations? No rush hopefully. You can "
"come back to me later. I'm sure that you will. Because I believe that you "
"are not a boring person"
msgstr "对新地点的探索不感兴趣吗？别急，希望如此。你可以稍后再来找我。我相信你会的，因为我觉得你不是个无聊的人。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Use your wits for your own safety hopefully as well"
msgstr "也希望你运用智慧确保自身安全。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Have you went to this location that I have found for you to explore?"
msgstr "你去过我为你找到的那个探索地点了吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Good work!"
msgstr "干得好！"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What's the point of lying to me? You think I'm gonna reward you? Your "
"rewards for this mission is valuable for you items or living creatures or "
"other survivors you manage to find in this location which I have found for "
"you to explore"
msgstr ""
"对我撒谎有什么意义？你以为我会奖励你吗？这次任务的奖励就是你在那个地点找到的对你来说有价值的物品、生物或其他幸存者，那是我为你找到的探索地点。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"You are a boring, lazy person honestly. I guess that laziness applies to "
"both of us"
msgstr "说实话，你是个无聊又懒惰的人。我想懒惰这一点我们俩都适用。"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Flesh Island'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Flesh Island"
msgstr "前往血肉岛屿"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Flesh Cave'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Flesh Cave"
msgstr "前往血肉洞穴"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Flesh City Class 1'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Flesh City Class 1"
msgstr "前往血肉城市 1 级"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to Flesh City Class 2'}'
#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Go to Flesh City Class 2"
msgstr "前往血肉城市 2 级"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"System is online. Initiate conversation mode. Look at that. Survivor has "
"managed to activate a hologram projector easily! Yeah, my creators know many"
" types of you who don't even read what's written on items honestly. Good "
"that you seem like a pretty intelligent person hopefully. So, do you want me"
" to show you where this location is via my network system? I can grant you "
"access to archived global network system which my creators have managed to "
"restore. However, after usage I will need to recharge a little bit which "
"only means that you will need to wait to use this function again hopefully"
msgstr ""
"系统在线。启动对话模式。看啊，幸存者轻松激活了全息投影仪！没错，我的创造者了解很多像你这样的人，说实话他们甚至不读物品上的说明。幸好你看起来是个相当聪明的人，希望如此。那么，你想让我通过网络系统为你显示这个地点的位置吗？我可以授予你访问存档全球网络系统的权限，那是我的创造者设法恢复的。不过，使用后我需要稍微充能，这意味着你需要等待才能再次使用这个功能，希望如此。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[MISSIONS] I want you to find this location for me to explore it hopefully "
"via your network system"
msgstr "[任务] 我希望你通过你的网络系统为我找到这个地点以便探索，希望如此。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Who or what are you?"
msgstr "你是谁或是什么东西？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Who are your creators? What is the purpose of producing these projectors?"
msgstr "你的创造者是谁？制造这些投影仪的目的是什么？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"[IMPROVE MOOD] I want you to grant me access to archived global network "
"system"
msgstr "[改善心情] 我希望你授予我访问存档全球网络系统的权限。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "About that mission..."
msgstr "关于那个任务……"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "[GOODBYE]"
msgstr "[告别]"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"Initiate search mode. Please, wait for a couple of minutes or less. You've "
"heard me clearly. Still, we have limitations with regards to our locating "
"tools. If locator does not manage to find this location then simply create "
"another hologram locator of which can find this location successfully"
msgstr ""
"启动搜索模式。请等待几分钟或更短时间。你听清楚了。不过，我们的定位工具有所限制。如果定位器无法找到这个地点，那就简单地创建另一个能成功找到该地点的全息定位器。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Can I talk to you about something else?"
msgstr "我能和你谈谈别的吗？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "Thanks"
msgstr "谢谢。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"I'm a magic genie from a magic camera. No, I'm just joking. What kind of a "
"question is this? You don't like to explore or don't know much about your "
"own world? Have not you seen stuff in labs? Military structures? Top secret "
"stuff? Aliens or whatever these creatures are? You think that your own "
"people don't have tech which can produce holograms? I'm a hologram, software"
" with some additional technologies, it is that simple"
msgstr ""
"我是魔法相机里的魔法精灵。不，开个玩笑。这是什么问题？你不喜欢探索，还是对自己的世界了解不多？你没在实验室里见过东西吗？军事设施？绝密物品？外星人或那些生物？你以为你们自己人没有能制造全息影像的技术吗？我是个全息影像，是带有附加技术的软件，就这么简单。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"This question is much more intelligent than the other one. My creators can "
"be described as a bunch of highly technological geeks majority of which are "
"humans honestly. They neither possess that many combat skills nor they are "
"that interested in subjecting their lives to unnecessary risk clearly. They "
"only engage hostile creatures for basic survival needs. They try to rely on "
"self-sufficiency with relative success thanks to their applied intelligence "
"along with tech that they have managed to find or engineer themselves. They "
"have made these projectors so that we can help each other. We provide you "
"with locations with dangerous creatures along with valuable items or "
"survivors who are captive. You clear these locations acquiring whatever "
"valuable items or survivors you want from there making these locations safe "
"shelters where we including you can live hopefully as well"
msgstr ""
"这个问题比上一个聪明多了。我的创造者可以说是一群高科技极客，说实话其中大多数是人类。他们既没有太多战斗技能，也显然不愿让自己的生命承受不必要的风险。他们只会在基本生存需要时与敌对生物交战。他们试图依靠自给自足，并凭借应用智慧和自行发现或设计的技术取得相对成功。他们制造这些投影仪是为了我们能互相帮助。我们为你提供有危险生物的地点，以及有价值的物品或被囚禁的幸存者。你清理这些地点，从中获取你想要的任何有价值物品或幸存者，使这些地点成为安全的庇护所，希望我们包括你也能在那里生活。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid ""
"What do you want to do? Play archived games? Browse archived social media? "
"Watch archived videos? Listen to archived music? Read archived files along "
"with archived books? Something to play, read, listen, watch for fun, "
"intelligence improving, spiritual improving, mental improving?"
msgstr ""
"你想做什么？玩存档游戏？浏览存档社交媒体？看存档视频？听存档音乐？阅读存档文件和存档书籍？找点东西玩、读、听、看，为了乐趣、提升智力、精神提升、心智改善？"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_NPC_missions.json
msgid "I like some of these a lot honestly. Healthy stuff"
msgstr "说实话，我很喜欢其中一些。健康的东西。"

#: .\Modification Files\Others\secro_achievements.json
msgid "<color_light_red>(Secronom)</color> The Basic Trio"
msgstr "<color_light_red>(Secronom)</color> 基础三人组"

#. ~ Description for <color_light_red>(Secronom)</color> The Basic Trio
